Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:27.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H247EFC&}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:30.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Piano Concerto  in A Minor Op. 54-1"]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:29.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only thing  I ever knew was cotton.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was hard work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:41.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you know cotton is ready  when the bud splits,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and the boll is star-shaped,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:46.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,like a big 0l' star in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Or like your big 0l' head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, is that some cotton?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:53.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that cotton?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I didn't mind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}'cause I got to spend all day  working with my daddy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:02:00.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hurry, take this picture.  - Take a picture of y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:03.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't everybody smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:08.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:16.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattie, come on,  I need your help in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:31.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pa... where he taking Ma?  - Get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:35.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil, come back here, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:43.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you lose your temper  with that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:47.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This his world.  We just living in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get on back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa, what you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,H9)'-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}'{\i0} Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- [gunshoq
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:05.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who you looking at?! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:09.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wants to go next?!  You get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:20.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you. Get some of the hands  to help dig a hole for his pa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:38.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have you  in the house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:46.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna teach you  how to be a house nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's coming.  - Yes'm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And quiet when you're serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:03.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want  to hear you breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:07.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The room should feel  empty when you're in it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:18.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was much nicer working  in the house than in the field.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy nigger, from the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:30.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:03.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I got older, I knew  I had to go before he killed me, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:12.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Part of me was scared to leave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:15.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the only world I ever knew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:27.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, I took Pa's watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:40.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:44.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My mama never  spoke much after that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew she'd miss me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:51.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I also knew she wanted me  to leave that place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:02.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And even though  Miss Annabeth never said it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:06.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew she'd miss me, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:23.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think God meant  for people to not have a family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:35.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Outside the cotton fields was even worse  than I thought it would be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:42.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one would give me a job  nor food nor a place to sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Any white man could kill  any of us at any time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and not {\i1}be{\i0} punished for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:08:00.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The law wasn't on our side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:05.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The law was against us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:15.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was hungry all the time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:46.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what can happen  to you, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:53.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:02.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:09.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have to lie  to the boss man about that window.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:13.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The good Lord say  we ain't supposed to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your ma and your pa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:22.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My ma crazy in the head,  and my pa got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you  some ham sandwiches
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and send you on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss will be here  in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:36.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunday's our busiest morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:41.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You looking for some help?  I know how to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:45.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You done broke our window,  you done stole our food,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and now you asking for a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:51.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in Macon,  I'm a house nigger, a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:57.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever use that word, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the white man's word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's filled With hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't your father  ever teach you any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:13.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Slow down.  - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You got to look through their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,See what it is they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Got it?  - Strokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:23.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah, I got it.  - Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:31.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,See what it is they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:35.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Anticipate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:48.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring a smile to the eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...of your principal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:05.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:10.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to save me them chitlins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why you like chitlins so much?  - 'Cause they're good eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:19.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The manager of Excelsior, in DC,  he came by yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He offered me a job as a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:25.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be paying you  top dollar, huh, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:28.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about taking it,  but I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:34.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too old to be leaving  North Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:38.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just fine right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:41.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him to hire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:44.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just now finding my way  around this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't ready for all them  highfalutin white people,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,all their fancy words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:52.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:56.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and the ones that we got  to show the white folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:59.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, to get up in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:03.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to make  them feel nonthreatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:07.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Use that, them fancy words  that I've taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:15.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,White folks up north,  they like some uppity coloreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:24.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I took that job  up in Washington, DC.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:29.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the most beautiful hotel  I'd ever seen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:37.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it wasn't  too presumptuous of me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to have prepared a few spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:42.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,after your long journey here  from Buffalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:47.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The best decision that court ever  made was to slow this whole mess down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:52.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nigger boys in school with white girls.  Who ever heard of such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:55.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Next thing you know,  they'd be fornicating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:13:01.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, this here is different.  We could start another Civil War.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:05.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil, what do you think about niggers  going to school with white children?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:08.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest with you,  Mr. Jenkins,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to not be too concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:14.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,with American or European politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor should you, Cecil.  They're all criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Earl Warren should be shot  and hanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:25.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That dumb son-of-a-bitch judge  is trying to integrate our schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:31.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Judge Warren is going to find  that quite challenging.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right, Cecil. Damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:39.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never in my life did I dream  I'd work in a place as fancy as this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:44.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never dreamed my life  could be so good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:56.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gloria and I met working  at the Excelsior.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was a maid at the hotel,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:02.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but now her only job  was raising our two boys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:08.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made sure that they  never laid eyes on a cotton field.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:15.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I got to pee.  - Not today. Don't try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Finish that homework.  - Where Louis at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:21.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's taking the trash out.  - Working late again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:24.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- How was your shift?  - Beats working for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you at night, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you got to pee?  Go on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:37.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wash your hands when you come  out of that bathroom, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:41.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good morning.  - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:47.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:51.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Dad.  - Hey, Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:54.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You all right?  - Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:57.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good.  - That woman whose son got killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:01.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,she's around doing speeches now.  What's her name, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:03.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mamie Till.  - Mamie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamie Till. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:09.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that story just  like it was yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,even though it was three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:15.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dis-damn-grace  what they did to that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for looking at a white woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,threw his body in the river,  killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't no older than Louis.  He was 14 at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Crazy white folks down South.  - Thanks, Ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,At least we got it  a little better in DC, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Still treating us bad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on down here, Charlie!  Wash your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Louis said we should stop  taking the white man's shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey.  - Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Watch your mouth.  - Watch your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:46.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Gaines' residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:49.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah. Hold on, Mr. Kidgan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:53.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's the boss man, Dad.  - What's he calling for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:57.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the white man call,  I always assume the worst.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would have put money on it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:05.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that I was getting laid off  or something that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:34.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Would you follow me, please?  - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Cecil Gaines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:45.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's a pleasure to meet you.  - You, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:48.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you political, Mr. Gaines?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- No, sir.  - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:12.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no tolerance  for politics at the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- How'd you find me?  - I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:17.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You served R.D. Warner  at the Excelsior Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He oversees operations  for the entire White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:23.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You made quite an impression.  - I don't recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:28.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Warner and myself make note  of potential staff around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler positions rarely open,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,as most stay on for 3O years or more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:35.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was quite surprised  when I got the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a surprise  for me, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:47.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,As the White House maTtre d',  I normally hire the butlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for saying this,  Mr. Fallows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly wouldn't want to  be hired under circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:58.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that would make you  feel uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You need butlers  that you've handpicked,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,men to your liking  that will fulfill your vision
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:08.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,of a proper White House staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:12.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:29.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... Louis XIII?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,These decanters are replicas
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:38.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,of metal flasks that were found  on the battlefield in Jarnac.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The Italians, they  know their wines,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:46.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Irish, they certainly know  how to make a great whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:51.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe the French  have a distinct advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:54.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,when it comes to Cognac.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:58.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Test vrai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:03.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you'll make  a good house nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you care  for a demitasse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:15.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it just be  me and Faye up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Faye  and a little scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:21.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to throw  a bash, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:30.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do  to this potato salad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what I did.  I put some dill in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:36.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,because I read in Woman's Day,  where pickles drown out the flavor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and dill bring up the flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:41.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's what you tasting right now.  - OK. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I like it.  - Make a difference, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:48.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl, you must be so proud of Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:51.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know he got that job hisself.  The White House called him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- he didn't call the White House.  - He's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You got a good man.  - She's fun, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:59.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like this one right here.  OI' sourpuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:03.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You still mad at me?  - I got reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:06.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't. I told you,  I went down to the numbers spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,played my little numbers,  got me some barbecue,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:11.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I went down...  I didn't even get nothing to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:16.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so... I'm so sick of these  numbers spot stories, Howard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How you expect me to believe you  was down at the numbers spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:20.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you believe it  or not don't mean it ain't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come on, stop this mess.  - You want to do this right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:24.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, y'all.  Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe it, you don't  have to believe it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come on, y'all.  - Such a shuckster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You really want to do this right now?  - Stop this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to pick on  somebody your own size.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We are here to celebrate,  so y'all could be nice just one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:37.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the lady.  Come on, get over here, let's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was out,  trying to make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:44.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Y'all need to get a room.  - What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that the truth?  Or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:49.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He drives me crazy. He just... Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't, uh...  You want to come to the room with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, where the boys at?  - They upstairs in the back room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:01.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys! Get on down here!  I need to see your face now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:03.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What y'all doing up there?  - Yes, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, when you gonna take me  to the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go  to the White House, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I want to go  to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't play with me now...  - When you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The White House,  now that's a big step up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ooh!  - Yeah, it's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:22.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl, you up in that house now!  I want to hear all the stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how many stories  you gonna hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,'cause they done swore him  to some kind of secret code,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:31.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- and he can't tell me nothing.  - No. Girl, you give it to him right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:35.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mm-hm! He'll tell you everything.  - That's the key right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:36.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you hear her?  - Who you been giving it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:42.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you was at home,  I could be giving it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know  what you talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:46.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys, y'all better bring  y'all little narrow butts down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:49.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Here they come.  - Called y'all 19 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:51.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys, stop running through this house.  You know better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:56.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Elroy! Get over here.  Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:00.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:04.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Tell them... Tell them what  you gonna be when you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:07.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to work at the White  House just like Mr. Gaines.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:09.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ah, that's my boy.  - Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:11.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:13.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Louis! What you gonna be  when you grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:16.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna work at  the White House like your daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:21.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't know.  - I'll tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:23.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew exactly what I wanted  to be when I was 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:27.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a number runner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:35.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Cecil Gaines.  I'm the new butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:37.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:39.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are 16 full-time maids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:42.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have six butlers,  four carpenters, two painters,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:45.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}seven electricians,  three dishwashers, three doormen,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:48.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,a {\i1}full kitchen staff, including pastry  chef and three full-time calligraphers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.53,0:22:51.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Two painters, seven  electricians, nine engineers...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:53.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Warner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:58.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Mr. Warner, wanted to thank you  for the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:23:00.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to work in the White House...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:09.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:14.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, I'm Cecil Gaines.  I'll be working with you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:16.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gaines,  please don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come on.  - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:21.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, when lifting a plate,  never scrape the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:25.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Never listen  or react to conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:29.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- The room should feel as...  - Empty when I'm in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:33.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So then she says...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:37.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she says, "Stick..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:39.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"CK-"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:41.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she starts  screaming and yells,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:45.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stick your whole hand in!"  So I put my whole hand in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she yells out,  "Put both hands in!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:50.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"OK!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:52.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she screams,  "Now clap!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:55.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I say, "I can't."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:57.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks up, smiles and says,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:24:00.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"See, I told you my..."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:01.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.87,0:24:03.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there he is!  Heard you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:05.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's your name?  - Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:07.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Cecil Gaines.  - That ain't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.24,0:24:11.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Carter Wilson, head butler.  Don't worry about Big Mo behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:13.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That brother will steal your wallet  before you even knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:16.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This brother in the mirror over here,  his name's James Holloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's my second in command.  - James.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.78,0:24:19.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Jackie Robinson or Willie Mays?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.82,0:24:21.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you shake  the man's hand first
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.19,0:24:23.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,before you start asking difficult  questions like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know  where the man's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:27.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look like the jury's still  out on that one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.76,0:24:30.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.  Fancy Freddie give you the tour yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.16,0:24:33.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He did.  ls the Dodgers still... still losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.47,0:24:35.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to answer that question  if Carter over here
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.97,0:24:37.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,stop running his nasty mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.67,0:24:40.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the shit  and let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.84,0:24:43.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ain't That a Kick in the Head"]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.26,0:25:05.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ready.  - Lord, help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.48,0:25:21.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be nervous, man.  Just go on and get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.39,0:25:32.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear nothing,  you see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.56,0:25:34.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You only serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.51,0:25:56.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Send federal troops to Little Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.98,0:25:59.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes to it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.09,0:26:04.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see any situation where  I'd send federal troops to the South.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.59,0:26:08.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever. Could cause another Civil War.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.93,0:26:14.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, if the federal government  doesn't enforce Brown, then who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.87,0:26:16.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The South must comply with the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.67,0:26:19.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just gonna take some time  to adjust, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.51,0:26:21.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.54,0:26:25.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but if Faubus continues to block the  Negro children, then what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.68,0:26:28.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We must enforce  the Constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.21,0:26:30.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Faubus more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.72,0:26:32.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,With a little persuading,  he'll back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.55,0:26:35.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We just want to move slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.43,0:26:44.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- How'd it go?  - I almost shit myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.87,0:26:49.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I dated a girl once. Every time  I hit her, she shit herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.24,0:26:52.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?  - Got no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.81,0:26:55.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shut up.  - You shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.01,0:26:57.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I put a towel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.35,0:27:00.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know, Marcella said  the very same thing last night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.81,0:27:03.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just before I put her to sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.72,0:27:12.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}Wow. You put her...{\i0}  {\i1}- Just like I did Ed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.09,0:27:16.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd do it real quick.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.33,0:27:23.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}'{\i0} See you!  - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.17,0:27:27.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang...  Got the popcorn all over the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.61,0:27:29.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's gonna kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.34,0:27:31.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.54,0:27:32.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi, Mr. Gaines.  - Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.91,0:27:35.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Elroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.35,0:27:38.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Louis, I told you about letting these  kids watch that show.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.79,0:27:41.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too scary.  They're too young for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.15,0:27:43.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.49,0:27:45.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All you got to do is smile pretty,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.13,0:27:46.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and a man will forget  everything he ever learned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.79,0:27:48.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where your mama at?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.53,0:27:51.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gloria tried staying up,  but she went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.30,0:27:53.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Elroy, ain't nobody  asked you nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.30,0:27:55.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your butt home before  your mama come up in here
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.14,0:27:56.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and whup the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.44,0:27:57.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come on, Dad.  - Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.74,0:27:59.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bye.  - Turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.95,0:28:10.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go stomping up the stairs,  wake your mama up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.69,0:28:21.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.33,0:28:24.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that that Mamie Till stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.40,0:28:28.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I want to go to this.  - Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.74,0:28:33.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.91,0:28:36.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no good can come of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.41,0:28:38.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you heard what Mama said?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.51,0:28:39.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That mess right there  happened down South.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.78,0:28:42.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- This could have been me.  - It happened down South.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.72,0:28:45.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I got out of there so we  could have us a better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.02,0:28:48.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm working for the white  man, make things better for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.19,0:28:50.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And not just any white man, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.09,0:28:53.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Put the lights off. Go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.24,0:29:13.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have your chicken soup,  Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.45,0:29:15.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just set it on the table, Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.28,0:29:17.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.22,0:29:23.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever complete school, Cecil?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.62,0:29:26.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't go to school,  Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.43,0:29:28.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I grew up on a cotton farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.80,0:29:31.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I grew up on a farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.30,0:29:33.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any children?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.70,0:29:35.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, I have two sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.70,0:29:37.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they go  to an all-colored school?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.81,0:29:41.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.45,0:29:49.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.28,0:29:51.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,State Guard just blocked  all the colored kids again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.42,0:29:54.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Faubus promised me the guards  would escort the kids in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.35,0:29:56.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Governor of Arkansas lied,  Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.72,0:30:01.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong with him?  Why is he forcing me to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.80,0:30:08.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.30,0:30:11.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next move  needs to be bold and swift.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.81,0:30:18.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have today  issued an executive order{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.44,0:30:21.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}directing the use of troops  under federal authority{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.78,0:30:25.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to aid in the execution  of federal law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.59,0:30:28.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}at Little Rock, Arkansas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.32,0:30:30.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This became necessary...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.29,0:30:33.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the president  sent those troops down to Little Rock,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.19,0:30:38.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was the first time I ever seen a  white man stick his neck out for us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.30,0:30:44.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told Louis that the president was  gonna make things better for us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.60,0:30:48.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All graduations are long.  She was so nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.24,0:30:50.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make  some potato salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.34,0:30:52.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now he could see that I knew  what I was talking about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.81,0:30:55.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful.  I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.18,0:30:59.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thanks, Mama.  - That hat looks stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.02,0:31:01.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.66,0:31:07.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Proud of you, too.  - Dad, did you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.13,0:31:09.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start something in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.36,0:31:13.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see one white kid  in my school?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.01,0:31:26.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why couldn't Louis see that  the president made things better for us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.38,0:31:28.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you.  - Cookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.08,0:31:29.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Cookies.  - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.85,0:31:32.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.26,0:31:41.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I told you  we was gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.23,0:31:43.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot miss this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.00,0:31:46.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, Lord have mercy.  - Wait, a sec. Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.07,0:31:48.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?  - Got to say good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.87,0:31:51.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bus can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.17,0:31:58.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Tennessee is  a long ways away, Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.48,0:32:00.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisk is a really  good school, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.98,0:32:03.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You can change your mind  and go to Howard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.58,0:32:07.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe you are still  talking about Howard University.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.39,0:32:11.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's going to Fisk.  - I know, I know. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.49,0:32:14.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just so far away, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.06,0:32:17.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's the point.  - What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.13,0:32:20.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a cigarette, and don't  tell me you don't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.87,0:32:23.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't have one.  - Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.67,0:32:27.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You know you want to cry, punk.  - Not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.47,0:32:30.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look under your mattress.  I left you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.54,0:32:34.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can't protect him down South.  - The South has changed, Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.28,0:32:35.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too young for Playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.72,0:32:37.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The South ain't what it  was when you was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:40.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, Louis is leaving me  his filthy magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.05,0:32:42.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stop lying on your brother.  - Why you slapping him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.06,0:32:43.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one with the magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.82,0:32:47.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I love you, Mama.  - I love you, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.26,0:32:49.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I love you, Louis.  - I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.33,0:32:53.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I made you ham sandwiches.  - Thanks, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.33,0:32:56.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.84,0:33:01.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.35,0:33:10.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.68,0:33:14.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.25,0:33:16.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.86,0:33:19.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to go, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.30,0:33:28.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.67,0:33:34.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, you call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.41,0:33:36.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right.  - All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.38,0:33:38.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.12,0:33:47.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.83,0:33:57.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.57,0:34:08.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Remind me again why  we're doing this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.74,0:34:11.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody? Tell me?  That look like a mugging to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.74,0:34:14.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- that's what that looks like.  - This is the art of French baking.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.35,0:34:17.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Negro, please.  "Art of French baking."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.78,0:34:20.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is absolutely nothing.  That's what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.02,0:34:22.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't...  - Boy's always so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.79,0:34:24.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to play with it?  I'll play with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.82,0:34:26.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Play With it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.73,0:34:29.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be good if it had a little...  a little nipple on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.76,0:34:31.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.20,0:34:33.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you play. You jiggle it.  You shake it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.40,0:34:34.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.87,0:34:38.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening,  Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.74,0:34:42.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like a tasty treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.61,0:34:44.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.71,0:34:47.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you all something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.65,0:34:53.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.15,0:34:55.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say anything negative
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.05,0:34:58.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,about that Kennedy boy.  I'm sure he's a real nice fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.42,0:35:01.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really want that  spoiled rich son-of-a-bitch fuck
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.53,0:35:04.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to be your next president?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.67,0:35:08.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.07,0:35:14.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cheer for you,  Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.97,0:35:17.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.88,0:35:22.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you something,  in all candor,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.55,0:35:27.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,as members of the Negro community,  what are your biggest concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.79,0:35:33.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on now, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.89,0:35:36.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.76,0:35:40.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Holloway, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.60,0:35:44.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Well, since you asked, sir...  - I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.44,0:35:48.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The colored help gets paid almost  4O percent less than the white help.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.57,0:35:50.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is that right?  - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.78,0:35:55.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's very difficult for  the colored staff to be promoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.12,0:35:59.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what. When I'm president,  I'm gonna look into getting you boys
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.29,0:36:01.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the raises and  the promotions you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.19,0:36:04.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That... that would be swell, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.46,0:36:08.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You got my word on that.  - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.43,0:36:10.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you tell your people  to vote for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.33,0:36:11.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's exactly  what's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.70,0:36:15.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that to somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.06,0:36:42.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, you don't  want to date nobody?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.16,0:36:43.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,After all these guys  that come after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.50,0:36:47.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Girl, please. I'm just...  - Like that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.07,0:36:50.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about you and Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.04,0:36:51.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on,  tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.50,0:36:53.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'all seemed happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.31,0:36:56.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I can't even have a normal  conversation with you, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.08,0:37:08.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey.  - You looking for love, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.36,0:37:13.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we call the Lawson workshop,  the love school.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.66,0:37:18.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is that what you're looking for?  - That's why I came to Fisk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.23,0:37:21.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.40,0:37:28.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm Carol Hammie.  - Louis Gaines.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.94,0:37:31.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.21,0:37:35.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You a country boy, ain't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.51,0:37:37.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a doctor. What does your dad do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.78,0:37:40.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.85,0:37:43.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You were gonna need help  finding this place anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.52,0:37:45.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...nor can you sustain it  over a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.39,0:37:47.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Really?  - This requires time, commitment,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.76,0:37:49.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,dedication, discipline and focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.36,0:37:52.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And we are measuring our  accomplishments in waves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.57,0:37:54.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a fly-by-night affair.  This doesn't happen over a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.93,0:37:58.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This requires a fierce discipline,  which is what we've been discussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.34,0:38:00.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you measure these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.31,0:38:02.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We go back, and we look  at somebody like Gandhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.91,0:38:05.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Together, we are gonna study  and examine Gandhi's techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.88,0:38:08.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What has been so effective  in South Africa, so effective in India,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.95,0:38:11.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,for his own people and others,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.62,0:38:14.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're gonna employ it  right here, in Nashville.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.62,0:38:18.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're gonna form an army.  You and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.42,0:38:21.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This army has one weapon.  That weapon is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.43,0:38:23.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I am of the... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.33,0:38:25.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If our only weapon is love,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.67,0:38:28.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and then their weapons  are weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.00,0:38:31.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I mean, isn't that dangerous?  - Oh, you can be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.67,0:38:34.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If anybody's uncomfortable with that,  you know where the door is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.07,0:38:37.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that sounds  provocative, but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.98,0:38:43.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, kids.  It's show time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.39,0:38:46.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Function at the Junction"]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.70,0:39:05.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gandhi has demonstrated for us  that the brown man,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.60,0:39:08.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,in his native land, or anywhere  that he's being oppressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.41,0:39:12.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...can pull himself out of segregation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.31,0:39:14.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,with patience, with persistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.98,0:39:18.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,with intelligence and thought,  with discipline...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.19,0:39:24.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and a bit  of a sense of humor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.50,0:39:35.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know y'all can't sit here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.53,0:39:37.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We would like to be served, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.90,0:39:40.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is unprecedented,  what we're talking about,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.74,0:39:44.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it{\i0} needs a patience  that none of us have ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.01,0:39:46.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You can order food  in the colored section,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.05,0:39:48.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not gonna be  serving you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.25,0:39:51.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We are organized.  We have a leader with every group.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.88,0:39:54.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have lookouts  with pocket change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.59,0:39:56.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the local phone numbers  for ambulances ready,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.42,0:39:59.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when one wave comes  off that lunch counter, what follows?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.53,0:40:01.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A whole 'nother wave of Negro students{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.36,0:40:03.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}sitting at that lunch counter,  blowing their mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.50,0:40:06.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We would like  to be served, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.44,0:40:12.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, who wants to role-play?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.20,0:40:14.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Jim, I need your help over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.67,0:40:16.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, y'all know you're  not supposed to sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.68,0:40:19.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Attack.  - Get up, nigger! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.61,0:40:21.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.21,0:40:23.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So do whatever it takes  to break their spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.55,0:40:25.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come on, get up, nigger.  - Use the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.82,0:40:27.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hear "nigger" coming  out of your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.29,0:40:29.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I need to hear "coon."  - I don't feel comfortable saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.19,0:40:31.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to get yourself prepared  and to get her prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.96,0:40:34.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So let me hear it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.03,0:40:37.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nigger.  - Louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.40,0:40:39.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Say the words like you mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.13,0:40:41.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nigger.  - Louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.10,0:40:42.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a nigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.40,0:40:46.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be sitting  in the colored seating.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.21,0:40:48.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not for you,  you cannot be served here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.31,0:40:50.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to do as you're told  and sit in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.61,0:40:52.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You are a nigger.  - Make her believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.78,0:40:54.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't believe you.  - You're a nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.48,0:40:55.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that's where  the colored people sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.78,0:40:59.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You see these people over here?  They're in their section over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.39,0:41:02.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You coon ass!  Get up, you nigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.92,0:41:06.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want us to shop  in this establishment, make them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.23,0:41:08.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Robert, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.58,0:41:26.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nigger lover, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.58,0:41:28.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get up, monkey. Get up!  - What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.78,0:41:31.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.78,0:41:34.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This says "whites only."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.45,0:41:37.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, nigger. Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.36,0:41:43.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Coons here?  - What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.50,0:41:45.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Does it say "coons?"  - "Whites only."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.40,0:41:50.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't belong here with them.  This? What is this, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.34,0:41:52.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Does it say "coons" here, huh?  - What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.94,0:41:56.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pay attention.  - No, this is whites only.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.21,0:41:58.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't belong here at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.84,0:42:01.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you reading?  I didn't know niggers could read.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.05,0:42:02.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, stupid?  You're a nigger lover now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.75,0:42:04.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, you nigger!  Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.85,0:42:07.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Look at me!  - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.02,0:42:10.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You disrespectful monkey. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.19,0:42:12.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?  You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.29,0:42:13.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.83,0:42:16.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.23,0:42:21.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up! Get up, you nigger!  Look at me! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.73,0:42:24.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That up there or is that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.17,0:42:28.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.64,0:42:31.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- but you have to decide.  - I was a nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.92,0:42:46.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go back to where you came from!  - Here, you want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.01,0:43:08.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the niggers are better  off in their own schools{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.88,0:43:10.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}than they are in the white schools.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.38,0:43:13.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- To serving our country.  - Serving our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.02,0:43:14.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.23,0:43:27.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel rich right now.  I like the way that tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.52,0:43:49.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They got no business out here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.32,0:43:50.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...better off in their  own schools than they are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.92,0:43:53.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in the white schools.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.33,0:43:59.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all sentenced to 3O days
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.16,0:44:00.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- in the countyjail.  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.77,0:44:04.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bailiff, get these  niggers out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.92,0:44:29.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Something special  is going on down here, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.03,0:44:35.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so special about  another colored man in jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.17,0:44:40.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What you doing  with my hard earned money, Pop?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.84,0:44:42.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.21,0:44:43.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to change  the way Negroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.64,0:44:45.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're breaking the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.35,0:44:49.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That judge just sentenced you  to 3O days in the county workhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.85,0:44:51.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You fixing to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.75,0:44:53.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't sit at any  lunch counter I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.35,0:44:55.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,then I might as well be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.15,0:44:57.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- We're fighting for our rights.  - Rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.29,0:44:58.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are you talking about?  - We're trying to change
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.69,0:45:00.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the nation's consciousness  toward the American Negro.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.23,0:45:01.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Them postcards you've been sending me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.66,0:45:04.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're a damn liar.  - I have been in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.57,0:45:08.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.67,0:45:11.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you into this world,  I can take you out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.94,0:45:47.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Y'all been able to talk to him?  - Talk to who?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.47,0:45:51.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Louis.  - Yeah, we talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.61,0:45:54.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Said he's joined something  called the "Freedom Riders,"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.28,0:45:56.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever the hell  that's supposed to mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.98,0:45:58.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.55,0:46:00.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I been fixing to trying to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.72,0:46:02.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I do,  Cecil get all riled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.99,0:46:05.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't know when  that's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.12,0:46:07.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fixing to trying."  See, that's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.63,0:46:10.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You got to stop trying,  and you just got to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.73,0:46:13.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He take you  to the White House yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.40,0:46:17.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Cecil say we're going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.24,0:46:19.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cecil say, Cecil say."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.97,0:46:23.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Four years. That's what makes  you a little bit gullible, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.78,0:46:26.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.  I don't understand why he can't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.08,0:46:28.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- get the president to do something.  - See, Gina, that's your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.51,0:46:30.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You just say stupid stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.92,0:46:35.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,President got more to do than be  thinking about Louis' foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.49,0:46:39.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,  why don't you just shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.12,0:46:42.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a mess.  Be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.63,0:46:45.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you  you could tell me to shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.76,0:46:47.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Well...  You...  - Go get me a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.93,0:46:50.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.20,0:46:56.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I personally think Louis is  gonna get every one of us killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.18,0:46:59.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They coming to get us.  They coming to get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.01,0:47:02.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He crazy like his mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.51,0:47:05.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant it in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.85,0:47:09.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!  I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.35,0:47:11.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.39,0:47:13.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.53,0:47:19.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I received also a wire from  President Eisenhower, which says...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.10,0:47:22.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The president lives  at the White House{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.30,0:47:25.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}until the moment the next one  is sworn in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.70,0:47:28.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the staff has exactly two hours{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.54,0:47:33.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}during the inauguration ceremony,  to move the old president out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.41,0:47:35.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and move the new one in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.91,0:47:40.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They say  this new white boy's smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.79,0:47:43.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to get my  butt home to Gloria.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.09,0:47:45.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause these hours,  they're killing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.76,0:47:47.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How's your boy doing, Cecil?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.53,0:47:51.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, the president's arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.53,0:47:56.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- OK.  - Where shall we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.94,0:47:58.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.  This end, maybe over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.57,0:48:00.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you.  - Right this way, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.21,0:48:03.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello, everyone.  - Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.18,0:48:06.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I am thrilled to be  working with all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.48,0:48:08.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,over the next four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.35,0:48:11.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight years, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.08,0:48:14.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see who wears  the pants around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.25,0:48:18.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna remember any  of your names, but I'm gonna try.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.06,0:48:20.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Jessie. It's a good thing you're here  'cause I'm gonna forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.26,0:48:23.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you. This is Lorraine.  - Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.20,0:48:24.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. President.  - How are you, James?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.80,0:48:26.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Carter.  - Pleasure, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.00,0:48:27.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Carter.  - This is Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.70,0:48:29.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pleasure to meet you, Mr. President.  - How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.33,0:48:30.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- William.  - Mrs. Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.64,0:48:32.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Greg.  - How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.74,0:48:34.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Winslow.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.07,0:48:36.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. She's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.28,0:48:39.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure to meet you,  Miss Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.24,0:48:41.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Miles.  - Miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.51,0:48:45.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that on your breath,  Gloria? Stop, OK. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.02,0:48:46.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's that?  - Baby, that's gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.82,0:48:49.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can smell it from here.  - It said "Addison's disease."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.82,0:48:51.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. Stop it, will you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.29,0:48:54.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take Charlie  to the dentist today?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.90,0:49:00.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody at the White House  got Addison's disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.43,0:49:05.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did not take Charlie  to the dentist today.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.40,0:49:08.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And what you asking me about it for?  You never home.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.37,0:49:11.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you gonna act like you gonna  take Charlie to the dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.01,0:49:14.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't never here.  I don't know how you gonna take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.11,0:49:16.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,His teeth fall out,  waiting on you to take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.65,0:49:21.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go to bed, Gloria.  I'll take him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.09,0:49:24.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How many pairs of shoes  does she have?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.36,0:49:30.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, how many pairs of shoes  does Mrs. Jackie Kennedy have?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.46,0:49:33.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell do I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.54,0:49:39.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in that 0l' White House  day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.24,0:49:41.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought you knew everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.84,0:49:47.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in,  trying to tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.11,0:49:49.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Worried about me drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.98,0:49:52.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You ought to be worried  about your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.52,0:49:55.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boy's in jail, Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.15,0:49:59.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boy's in jail,  and you can't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.13,0:50:03.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You don't see I'm here,  trying to talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.33,0:50:10.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you wish I spoke French,  just like Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.00,0:50:12.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Jackie Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.64,0:50:16.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Que sera, sera.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.81,0:50:19.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.64,0:50:22.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You like the way she talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.88,0:50:25.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil,  you hear me talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.05,0:50:28.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.57,0:50:47.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bobby told the president{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.01,0:50:49.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they shouldn't be worried about  the Negro sit-ins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.81,0:50:53.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Polls show the US  does not support civil rights.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.35,0:50:57.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Told you that white boy was smooth.  A little too smooth for my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.16,0:51:07.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Cecil, how's your boy doing?  - Out of jail, says he's back in school,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.09,0:51:09.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think he's doing  that freedom riding thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.43,0:51:12.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Gloria doing  with that drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.20,0:51:15.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,She's hanging-
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.10,0:51:21.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that cat  that's playing is a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.27,0:51:25.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pablo Casals, world famous.  - Course he's world famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.24,0:51:27.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You think Mrs. Kennedy  is gonna have, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.18,0:51:29.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,some backwoods country fiddle  band playing out there for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.61,0:51:31.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Man.  - Why don't you start a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.15,0:51:32.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you can go out there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.92,0:51:35.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what, in fact,  let's all start a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.22,0:51:37.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play the bongos.  What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.16,0:51:39.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I play a mean... skin flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.62,0:51:43.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- ♪ Babalu.  - Casals is a righteous soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.30,0:51:46.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He refuses to play in any country  that recognizes Franco's regime.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.73,0:51:49.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Franco?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.07,0:51:52.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Forget it, man.  - Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.90,0:51:56.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. You're ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.59,0:52:09.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Carol, are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.65,0:52:12.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want me to put my head  on your shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.39,0:52:13.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.76,0:52:15.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not putting my head  on your shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.13,0:52:16.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.50,0:52:20.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever been  on a freedom bus before?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.93,0:52:22.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- No, it's my first time.  - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.40,0:52:24.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- How's your boyfriend feel about that?  - My boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.44,0:52:28.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I mean,  this must upset him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.31,0:52:30.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You being on this bus down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.14,0:52:32.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't have a boyfriend.  - You don't have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.41,0:52:35.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you not have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.98,0:52:40.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You want some peanuts?  - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.99,0:52:43.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You like peanuts or...?  - I don't like peanuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.62,0:52:46.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm too hot to eat.  - Hey, can I have some of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.42,0:52:49.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Long bus ride.  - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.97,0:52:57.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Louis, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.91,0:53:07.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's a cross. It's a cross.  - Driver, turn! Turn the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.02,0:53:12.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.72,0:53:20.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Niggers, get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.39,0:53:24.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nigger, go home! Nigger, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.61,0:54:17.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.  Everybody out!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.79,0:54:29.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"In an old house in Paris{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.19,0:54:32.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that was covered with vines...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.56,0:54:38.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...lived 12 little girls  in two straight lines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.57,0:54:42.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The smallest one  was Madeline."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.27,0:54:45.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Like Caroline.  - Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.14,0:54:48.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"She was not afraid of mice."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.05,0:54:51.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do people ride  in the freedom bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.85,0:54:56.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Bobby told my daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.86,0:55:01.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that the freedom bus  exploded today.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.70,0:55:08.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't tell you  if I walked off the bus{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.00,0:55:12.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or if I crawled off  or if someone pulled me off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.64,0:55:15.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know if my boy  was dead or alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.61,0:55:18.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I got off the bus,  a man came up to me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.51,0:55:20.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I'm coughing and strangling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.61,0:55:22.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and he said, "Boy, you all right?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.48,0:55:25.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I nodded my head,  and the next thing I knew,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.98,0:55:27.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was on the ground.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.82,0:55:32.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He had hit me with{\i0} a {\i1}baseball bat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.12,0:55:34.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.69,0:55:38.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Dad.  I'm in Mississippi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.43,0:55:41.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought you was in Alabama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.03,0:55:44.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We spent two weeks in jail  there, now we're in Mississippi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.47,0:55:46.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to listen  to me, Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.87,0:55:49.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.24,0:55:52.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know we ain't seen eye to eye,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.21,0:55:55.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but your mama,  she wants you home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.92,0:56:00.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- They're keeping me.  - How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.32,0:56:02.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where is he?  {\i1}- I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.22,0:56:04.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They said three months.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.09,0:56:07.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I get out,  I'm gonna take another ride.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.03,0:56:10.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are you talking about?  - What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.16,0:56:11.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to him.  Give me that phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.90,0:56:14.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is my right to ride that bus.  That is my legal right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.83,0:56:18.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I will exercise my rights  as an American citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.17,0:56:21.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}American citizen.  What you talking about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.37,0:56:23.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what  they're gonna do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.27,0:56:25.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna lynch you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.88,0:56:29.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and then they're gonna throw  your little ass in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.85,0:56:31.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.42,0:56:35.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, then they're just  gonna have to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.52,0:56:37.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Negro  and white in Birmingham{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.26,0:56:41.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}have been building up  to scenes with clashes, like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.26,0:56:44.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The situation was perilously  close to an explosion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.76,0:56:47.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrests were made in mass lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.77,0:56:50.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone charged  with the same offense...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.37,0:56:53.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.87,0:56:55.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for your signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.74,0:56:58.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}City police were  carrying out their pledge{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.11,0:57:00.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to fill their jails to  capacity if necessary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.61,0:57:03.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are acting  according to the wishes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.21,0:57:06.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what country  I'm looking at.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.72,0:57:11.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...tone of the city for many years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.37,0:57:28.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.38,0:57:36.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Residents here  have taken to the streets{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.38,0:57:38.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in Birmingham, Alabama,  to bring attention to their efforts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.88,0:57:41.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}against the segregation  of black Americans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.75,0:57:45.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is following earlier boycotts  in Birmingham to pressure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.96,0:57:50.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Louis, man, that little  nigga might be onto something.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.66,0:57:56.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling him a nigga,  'cause he ain't no nigga.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.07,0:57:58.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.00,0:58:02.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's wrong with me is this.  - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.34,0:58:06.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's wrong with me.  This is wrong. This is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.34,0:58:09.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- We ain't been wrong yet.  - I can't do this to Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.75,0:58:12.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't doing it to Cecil.  I'm doing it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.48,0:58:15.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you out of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.19,0:58:19.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think God brought us  next to each other each day?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.36,0:58:22.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- God ain't got nothing to do with this.  - He put you right next door to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.36,0:58:25.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You always talking about how  lonely you are without Cecil
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.00,0:58:27.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,being at the White House,  and you need a man that can
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.50,0:58:30.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,appreciate the love and the  woman that you are, like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.94,0:58:33.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want your number-running  ass up out of my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.67,0:58:37.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,off of my sofa right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.18,0:58:39.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm through.  I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.88,0:58:41.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me make  a demonstration for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.55,0:58:43.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come here with  this bullshit crazy talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.65,0:58:45.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's not.  - Some more of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.52,0:58:48.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is you, right? You got  your direction that you move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.02,0:58:52.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What you doing with my hangers?  - This is you, and this is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.72,0:58:56.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we seem like we don't fit at all.  We just crash into each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.19,0:58:59.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But then when  you align things properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.80,0:59:01.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,like God putting you  next door to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.83,0:59:05.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,everything kind of works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.27,0:59:09.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if you slow down,  I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.28,0:59:12.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get your yellow  ass up out of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.98,0:59:15.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- We need each other.  - What I need is my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.85,0:59:19.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And not to be laying up here  in the gutter with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.43,0:59:34.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,On average, how many pills do  you think I take a day, Cecil?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.90,0:59:38.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,About... 103, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.54,0:59:45.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Help me up.  - Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.62,0:59:55.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your son is a Freedom Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.12,1:00:01.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in prison right now in Birmingham  with Martin Luther King.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.23,1:00:09.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.40,1:00:12.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...you know how he is, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.54,1:00:17.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing he's pretty beat up,  but based on his record,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.11,1:00:19.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,he must be used to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.78,1:00:25.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil, he's been arrested 16 times  over the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.89,1:00:30.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.13,1:00:37.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Will that be all, sir?  - That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.53,1:00:42.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I never understood
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.80,1:00:45.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,what you all really went through...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.27,1:00:49.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...until I saw that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.88,1:00:54.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother says these kids have...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.15,1:00:58.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...changed his heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.49,1:01:06.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They've changed mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.49,1:01:13.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fires of discord are burning  in every city North and South,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.53,1:01:16.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}where legal remedies  are not at hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.40,1:01:18.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Redress is sought in the streets,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.04,1:01:21.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in demonstrations,  parades and protests.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.84,1:01:24.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am therefore  asking the Congress{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.28,1:01:26.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to enact legislation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.31,1:01:29.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,giving all Americans the right  to be served in facilities
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.35,1:01:30.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,which are open to the public.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.85,1:01:33.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hotels, restaurants, theaters,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.75,1:01:36.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}retail stores  and similar establishments.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.92,1:01:40.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This seems to me to be  an elementary right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.36,1:01:42.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Its denial is  an arbitrary indignity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.83,1:01:47.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that no American in 1963  should have to endure, but many do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.33,1:01:50.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A great change is at hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.00,1:01:54.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And our task, our obligation,  is to make that revolution,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.41,1:01:59.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that change,  peaceful and constructive for all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.48,1:02:04.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those who do nothing are  inviting shame as well as violence...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.24,1:02:30.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Hey, Cecil.  Cecil, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.04,1:02:35.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.75,1:02:40.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.85,1:02:43.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They blew his...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.72,1:02:46.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...head off.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.09,1:02:53.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who are you talking about?  - Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.04,1:03:01.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}President Kennedy was shot{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.34,1:03:04.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as he drove from Dallas airport  to downtown Dallas...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.08,1:03:05.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They killed him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.31,1:03:08.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Governor Connally of Texas  in the car with him was also shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.85,1:03:11.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is reported that  three bullets rang out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.55,1:03:13.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Secret Serviceman has been...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.75,1:03:16.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They killed our man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.35,1:03:19.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"He's dead." Whether he  referred to President Kennedy or not{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.59,1:03:21.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is not yet known.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.46,1:03:24.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The president, cradled in the  arms of his wife, Mrs. Kennedy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.93,1:03:27.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was carried to an ambulance  and the car rushed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.63,1:03:29.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to Parkland Hospital outside Dallas...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.67,1:03:33.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mrs. Kennedy refused  to change her clothes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.50,1:03:38.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so that everybody could see  what they did to her husband.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.85,1:03:49.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last time  I saw that much blood{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.12,1:03:52.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was the day my daddy was killed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.63,1:04:04.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me how I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.17,1:04:43.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, what you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.71,1:04:48.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Want you to take this box  and put it in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.51,1:04:50.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Make sure you label it "trophies."  - This is Louis' stuff, Ma.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.85,1:04:52.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know he gonna be pissed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.52,1:04:54.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care nothing about  Louis being pissed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.39,1:04:56.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one pissed.  He ain't been here in three years.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.69,1:04:58.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you pissed, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.39,1:05:00.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't put that next  to myjarred okra either.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.22,1:05:02.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't nobody trying to smell  that stankin' okra.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.03,1:05:04.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you come back, I want  you to get me some fish food.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.85,1:05:25.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look what the president...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.72,1:05:27.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mrs. Kennedy gave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.55,1:05:30.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Belonged to the president.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.59,1:05:34.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gloria...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.39,1:05:37.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,President was killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.63,1:05:41.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about the president.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.73,1:05:43.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.77,1:05:46.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But you and that White House  can kiss my ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.27,1:05:48.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what  goes on in that house.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.21,1:05:50.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I care about what goes on in this house.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.19,1:05:57.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll Close My Eyes"]
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.78,1:06:34.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew that Gloria had been  unhappy for some time now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.15,1:06:38.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew that's probably  why she drank.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.36,1:06:43.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She wanted me to get along  better with Louis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.96,1:06:46.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know how.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.30,1:06:48.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.83,1:06:53.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could cut back them  long hours at the White House.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.14,1:06:55.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I did just that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.54,1:06:57.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How many pairs of shoes she got?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.81,1:07:00.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,She got about... 125.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.85,1:07:03.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- A hundred twenty-five pairs of shoes?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.51,1:07:08.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Put them in a line from the blacks  all the way to the whites.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.59,1:07:12.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll tell you what. Next time  there's a light on in an empty room,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.36,1:07:15.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fire every sorry son of a bitch  in this house. I mean it, Cecil!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.53,1:07:18.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to Texas and run the country  from a dirt shack if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.83,1:07:20.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.36,1:07:22.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think pays the  goddamned bills around here?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.10,1:07:23.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Idon%,butyou  know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.63,1:07:25.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.07,1:07:28.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.97,1:07:32.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Bird and I want you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.21,1:07:36.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Matches your eyes.  - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.42,1:07:40.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get it, Gloria.  - Do it, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.68,1:07:43.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Swim it! Go ahead, Gloria.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.25,1:07:48.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I see you, baby.  - You see me, babe? Put it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.26,1:07:50.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Paughs]
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.83,1:07:52.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it, Gloria.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.70,1:07:56.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Now that's what I'm talking about.  - Get it, girl! Shake it out! Get it!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.94,1:08:02.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Negro! Get out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.37,1:08:04.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Back there stinking up  my bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.14,1:08:05.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, Lord.  - Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.94,1:08:07.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.41,1:08:09.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.55,1:08:11.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.85,1:08:13.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get you some!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.92,1:08:17.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You know.  - That's your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.02,1:08:21.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my wig!  What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.63,1:08:24.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- This my good wig!  - Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.56,1:08:27.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sit down.  - We got the spades up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.40,1:08:29.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Brotherjust handling his business.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.03,1:08:30.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He can still do the splits,  I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.87,1:08:33.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,James told me  that Dr. King told the president
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.24,1:08:36.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that we would be going to the streets  down South for our right to vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.44,1:08:38.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Didn't you, baby?  - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.31,1:08:40.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell me  that Dr. King told the president
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.54,1:08:42.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that we was going down South  for our right to vote?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.75,1:08:45.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I ain't make that up.  - Is that what you heard?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.45,1:08:47.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That Dr. King ain't no joke,  with his little militant ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.75,1:08:50.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- She talking too damned much.  - Well, sound like somebody talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.15,1:08:51.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.42,1:08:54.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Leave my bird alone.  - Well, you know them three kids
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.06,1:08:56.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,got killed down there, trying to get  colored folks registered to vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.96,1:08:58.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want  Louis to go down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.46,1:09:00.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was  trying to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.06,1:09:01.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have  sent him down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.53,1:09:03.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I know.  - He is down there now,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.77,1:09:05.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and there ain't nothing  we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.80,1:09:07.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason  the president sent the FBI
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.51,1:09:08.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,is 'cause two of them were white.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.87,1:09:11.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Now who told you that?  - Yeah, who told her that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.94,1:09:15.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in one of them colored newspapers  from Baltimore. That all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.78,1:09:18.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,See, she getting smart now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.28,1:09:20.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, you think the president  ought to do something
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.58,1:09:23.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- about the Voting Rights bill?  - That ain't the trump.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.15,1:09:24.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,President Johnson  just passed the greatest piece
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.82,1:09:27.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,of civil rights legislation  since Lincoln freed the slaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.99,1:09:30.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be very difficult to  pass another bill anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.63,1:09:33.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's it.  - You see how my wife quizzes me?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.00,1:09:36.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I get it every day.  - Only, you got to know
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.13,1:09:38.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,how much to say,  when you cross the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.34,1:09:40.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You deal with your woman,  I'll deal with mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.04,1:09:42.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you tell your wife  what's going on over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.24,1:09:43.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- A!  - Aces!  - Damn!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.84,1:09:46.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be a king  in your own castle.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.14,1:09:48.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You hit the strip joint,  that's what I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.31,1:09:52.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, uh, Glo. Did you hear about  your neighbor, Howard?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.08,1:09:59.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Guy down on 8th Street,  caught him in bed with his wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.06,1:10:00.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Shot him dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.69,1:10:04.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shot him in the back.  - That's it. That's all of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.03,1:10:08.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, maybe he got  what he deserved.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.47,1:10:11.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sorry sap asses  got to realize{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.54,1:10:13.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the Negro ain't gonna take it no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.64,1:10:15.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This entire country is a tinderbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.61,1:10:19.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn tinderbox of nigger rage  just waiting to explode!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.21,1:10:21.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I want you all  to get on the phone,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.51,1:10:23.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,call the NAACP, CORE  and whoever else
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.88,1:10:25.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,will listen to your sorry asses
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.55,1:10:27.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and help me keep them Negroes  off the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.92,1:10:31.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Buck, I smell your ass from here!  What the hell are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.19,1:10:34.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.26,1:10:37.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil, get me some of  that goddamned prune juice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.10,1:10:46.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what to make  of Malcolm X.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.20,1:10:47.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what to make of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.87,1:10:50.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a better plan  in place than Dr. King.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.04,1:10:53.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone puts their hands on  you, put them in the cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.41,1:10:56.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- That a better plan?  - Ooh, We fixin' to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.71,1:10:58.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Claramay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.18,1:11:00.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good night.  - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.72,1:11:04.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.92,1:11:09.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You just mad 'cause he was  talking about your daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.03,1:11:11.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.10,1:11:13.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He was saying all that  stuff about house Negroes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.26,1:11:15.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you get mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.37,1:11:18.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad is not a house Negro.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.44,1:11:24.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- He a butler, ain't he?  - Don't talk about my dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.48,1:11:27.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't talk about your dad,  all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.01,1:11:29.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 'cause my daddy's  proud of what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.76,1:11:45.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.14,1:12:32.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everybody went to church to  raise money for the kids down in Selma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.41,1:12:37.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I didn't go. I wasn't gonna give  money to pay for my son to be killed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.39,1:12:48.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, them kids got beat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.26,1:12:53.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This one was so bad that the press  called it "Bloody Sunday."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.40,1:12:55.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They barely left Selma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.47,1:12:58.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They marched in small groups  through the city of Selma{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.24,1:13:00.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}and were not stopped...{\i0}  {\i1}- ...mortars and rockets...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.14,1:13:02.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...can pound Con Thien  around the clock{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.31,1:13:04.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with devastating effect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.11,1:13:05.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And our ground troops  cannot go into...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.94,1:13:07.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it was a different story.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.88,1:13:10.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mounted sheriff's deputies  helped to break up the column.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.71,1:13:12.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once the line was broken...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.58,1:13:15.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How are your boys, Cecil?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.79,1:13:27.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how my oldest is,  Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.40,1:13:29.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he might  be in Selma.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.83,1:13:32.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And, you know,  sometime I feel like
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.44,1:13:35.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,we're living in  two different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.97,1:13:39.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just want to keep him safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.41,1:13:43.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...marchers were  treated for tear gas burns,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.28,1:13:45.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}open wounds and broken bones.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.02,1:13:46.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One hospital treated...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.58,1:13:52.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every American citizen  must have an equal right to vote.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.46,1:13:56.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yet the harsh fact is that  in many places in this country,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.96,1:14:01.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}men and women  are kept from voting{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.53,1:14:04.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}simply because they are Negroes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.23,1:14:06.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Negroes?"
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.10,1:14:09.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did he start  calling us Negroes?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.64,1:14:12.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That nigger uses the word  "nigger" more than I use it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.91,1:14:15.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But really it's all of us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.68,1:14:20.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...who must overcome  the crippling legacy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.85,1:14:24.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}of bigotry and injustice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.05,1:14:27.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we shall overcome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.80,1:14:33.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First,  a barrage of cover fire,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.73,1:14:35.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and then a charge across the street.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.77,1:14:38.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Marines moved out from  the fortified Army compound{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.50,1:14:40.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}blitzed by the original attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.30,1:14:42.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, hey, LBJ!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.24,1:14:44.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How many kids  did you kill today?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.61,1:14:46.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey,hey,LBJ!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.81,1:14:48.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How many kids  did you kill today?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.71,1:14:50.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the ancient imperial city.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.38,1:14:53.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is to Vietnamese  what old Boston is to Americans,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.82,1:14:56.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}where many of its country's  leaders are born or educated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.82,1:14:59.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.86,1:15:03.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first sniper shots ricochet  around the thick walls of the building,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.16,1:15:07.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}taking the first casualties  of the first squad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.20,1:15:09.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The snipers may be  only two or three,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.57,1:15:11.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}invisible to the buildings  beyond the wall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.94,1:15:14.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there is also a machine gun  down the street to the left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.47,1:15:19.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. King, you might want to  lie down with that fever.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.84,1:15:24.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,President Johnson is making  a tragic error in Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.62,1:15:27.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Move over, big yellow.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.42,1:15:29.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why shouldn't we fight in Vietnam?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.69,1:15:32.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vietcong don't call us  "niggers," for one.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.06,1:15:39.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, how many of  your parents support the war?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.86,1:15:45.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my Lord.  Why do your parents support it?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.47,1:15:48.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't spoken about it specifically,  I just know they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.77,1:15:52.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what do your daddy do?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.08,1:15:55.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a butler.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.45,1:15:58.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The black domestic play an  important role in our history.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.78,1:16:01.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell you that  to make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.05,1:16:04.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Young brother, the black  domestic defy racial stereotypes
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.92,1:16:08.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,by being hardworking and trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.10,1:16:16.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He slowly  tears down racial hatred{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.13,1:16:22.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with his example of a strong work ethic  and dignified character.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.38,1:16:29.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, while we perceive the butler  or the maid to be subservient,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.48,1:16:34.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,in many ways, they are subversive,  without even knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.02,1:16:41.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come in, Cecil.  - Afternoon, Mr. Warner.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.10,1:16:47.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for seeing me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.88,1:17:04.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the colored...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.41,1:17:06.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the black staff
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.62,1:17:10.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,does just as much work  as the white staff,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.22,1:17:15.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that our salaries  should reflect our service, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.46,1:17:18.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Black" staff?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.40,1:17:23.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I also feel  that we should have...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.84,1:17:29.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...opportunities of advancement.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.11,1:17:31.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No black houseman
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.84,1:17:36.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,has ever been promoted  to the engineer's office.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.08,1:17:40.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very well liked here, Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.98,1:17:43.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're unhappy  with your salary or position,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.15,1:17:45.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,then I suggest you seek  employment elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.52,1:17:47.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- With all due respect...  - Don't let that Martin Luther King shit
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.69,1:17:52.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,fill your britches out.  Just remember where I found you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.00,1:18:02.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.45,1:18:10.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.86,1:18:22.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dr. Martin Luther King,  the apostle of non-violence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.23,1:18:26.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in the civil rights movement has been  shot to death in Memphis, Tennessee.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.23,1:18:28.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Police have issued  an All Points Bulletin{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.67,1:18:31.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for a well-dressed, young white  man seen running from the scene.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.87,1:18:34.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Officers also reportedly  chased and fired on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.84,1:18:38.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,a {\i1}radio-equipped car  containing two white men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.74,1:19:09.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know if I was  gonna get home alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.27,1:19:15.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the first time I felt like  I didn't belong in my own neighborhood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.05,1:19:17.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The whole world was changing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.98,1:19:21.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I didn't know where I fit in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.25,1:19:24.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dr. King has been a buffer  the last two years,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.89,1:19:27.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}between the black community  and the white community.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.29,1:19:28.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The white people do not know it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.76,1:19:31.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the white people's  best friend is dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.60,1:19:34.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The black people's leader, our Moses,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.26,1:19:37.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the once in a four-  or five-hundred year leader,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.63,1:19:40.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}has been taken from us  by hatred and bitterness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.30,1:19:42.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even as I stand at this hour,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.17,1:19:46.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cannot even allow hate  to enter my heart at this time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.78,1:19:50.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for it was sickness,  not meanness, that killed him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.62,1:20:33.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma... my room's pink.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.23,1:20:41.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get some more  of my sweet potatoes, Carol.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.46,1:20:43.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I use orange juice  when I make 'em,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.50,1:20:46.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that's what make 'em so... tart.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.40,1:20:48.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How long y'all been dating?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.74,1:20:50.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Five years.  - We're just friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.71,1:20:58.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is, uh,  all the rest of the students
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.38,1:21:01.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,are they getting involved  in politics, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.69,1:21:08.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a division.  Kind of a split, Ma.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.59,1:21:12.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A few of them,  like John Lewis, they're still...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.16,1:21:15.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I love John Lewis.  - How you know who John Lewis is?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.57,1:21:17.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause, honey,  I read {\i1}Jet{\i0} magazine.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.63,1:21:20.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not just sitting up there  sewing for you all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.70,1:21:22.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.51,1:21:26.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick and tired of getting  thrown in jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.24,1:21:28.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, that makes  two of us, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.91,1:21:32.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. King's philosophy ultimately  got him murdered.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.62,1:21:34.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked when we started,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.85,1:21:39.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but... now it's time to take  the next step, which is politics.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.06,1:21:40.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So y'all going  to the White House now?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.79,1:21:42.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, Louis going  to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.19,1:21:43.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know they ain't gonna  let you in there
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.73,1:21:45.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,with them nipples out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.30,1:21:47.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe one, but not both of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.53,1:21:51.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Nah, we're...  we're more grass roots.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.17,1:21:53.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,One-on-one with the community.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.64,1:21:55.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we have started  our own political party.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.91,1:21:58.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your party?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.41,1:21:59.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You like to party?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.94,1:22:04.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I like to party.  What's your party called?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.62,1:22:07.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Panther Party.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.78,1:22:12.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of name is that?  What's that stand for?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.26,1:22:15.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We... provide free breakfast  for children,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.09,1:22:19.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,free medical clinics, free clothing,  self-defense classes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.20,1:22:21.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And why y'all need self-defense?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.60,1:22:23.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't gettin' beat no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.61,1:22:31.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and your daddy saw a  wonderful movie the other night.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.11,1:22:32.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Reminded me so much of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.91,1:22:35.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.48,1:22:37.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the name  of that movie, honey?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.51,1:22:39.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the Heat of the Night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.32,1:22:46.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the Heat... of the Night,  with Sidney Poitier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.19,1:22:48.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord, Sidney Poitier.  I love Sidney Poitier.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.79,1:22:52.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sidney Poitier's a white man's fantasy  of what he wants us to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.33,1:22:56.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But his movies have him  fighting for equal rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.00,1:22:58.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Only in a way that's acceptable  to the white status quo.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.07,1:23:02.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ah.  - The brother can't act.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.11,1:23:04.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.07,1:23:05.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He just won the Academy Award.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.84,1:23:07.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's breaking down barriers  for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.98,1:23:11.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,By being white.  By acting white.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.98,1:23:15.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sidney Poitier is nothing but  a rich Uncle Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.15,1:23:20.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.12,1:23:22.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All puffed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.53,1:23:24.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,With your hat on your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.76,1:23:27.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in here,  saying whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.36,1:23:29.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Girlfriend belching at the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.13,1:23:31.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even feel  you gotta go to school,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.70,1:23:34.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,even though I gave you the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.31,1:23:38.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.74,1:23:43.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Louis.  I need you to get out of my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.55,1:23:47.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?  - Get the hell out of my house!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.35,1:23:48.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are you doing?  - Get on out!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.95,1:23:50.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's gotta go!  - No, Cecil, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.85,1:23:52.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can't take this no more!  - We ain't seen this boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.82,1:23:54.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't seen this boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.22,1:23:55.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna snatch the life  out of you, boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.56,1:23:57.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Now, everybody just sit down.  - I'm sorry, Mr. Butler,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.16,1:24:00.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to make  fun of your hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.36,1:24:04.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you are and  everything you have is...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.87,1:24:07.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...'cause of that butler.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.30,1:24:11.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you take that trifling  low-class bitch...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.58,1:24:15.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and get out of this house.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.19,1:24:32.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Sidney Poitier, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.66,1:24:36.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that{\i0} movie he {\i1}did?  Look Who's Coming to Dinner?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.83,1:24:38.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything ain't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.40,1:24:41.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Carol came to dinner.  - Hush, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.01,1:24:47.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Police took Louis the next day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.98,1:24:56.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'all gonna make me late for work.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.25,1:24:57.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Unc, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.89,1:24:59.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else I'm supposed to call  to bail him out?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.29,1:25:03.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What they got him in for this time?  Sit up!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.09,1:25:07.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Louis said they  stopped him just because.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.86,1:25:10.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.93,1:25:13.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wasn't going  to get beat no more, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.47,1:25:16.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...he got out the car  and he hit 'em back.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.27,1:25:19.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that little gal of his?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.34,1:25:21.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They put her in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.91,1:25:23.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.45,1:25:25.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.42,1:25:28.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This shit's gotta stop, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.09,1:25:32.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late for work.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.22,1:25:34.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell Louis I'm not his mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.29,1:25:37.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my money back.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.10,1:25:42.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.13,1:25:44.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.93,1:25:47.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Uncle Carter.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.27,1:25:50.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take all this Black  Panther shit somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.11,1:25:53.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm not them.  I want my money back, hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.11,1:25:56.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, sir.  - Every dime.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.01,1:26:01.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, sir.  - Hey, Unc... don't tell Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.93,1:26:12.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How you avoid all that sex  in prison?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.56,1:26:14.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they teach you that  with the Panthers?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.80,1:26:19.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They teach you how to... to sit...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.41,1:26:27.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- She been drinking again?  - No. She's sober.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.54,1:26:30.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,She ain't doing nothing but sewing  and feeding them damn fishes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.98,1:26:34.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Feed them more than she feed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.38,1:26:37.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You excited about  going back to Howard?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.02,1:26:40.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Excited about not going back.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.82,1:26:43.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.33,1:26:45.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.70,1:26:48.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlie, don't do this.  Don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.87,1:26:53.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- This country treats us like dogs!  - And do what? Don't do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.87,1:26:58.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You fight your country.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.71,1:27:01.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fight for my country.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.24,1:27:04.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I won't go to your funeral.  - Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.58,1:27:08.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I don't want you there  with all of that...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.35,1:27:12.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...black leather and latex,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.72,1:27:17.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,shining and taking away the attention  off of my pretty face in my casket.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.40,1:27:22.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they call you now, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.77,1:27:24.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shut up.  - Louise Gaines.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.57,1:27:26.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlie, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.07,1:27:30.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know every goddamn  domestic policy decision right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.04,1:27:31.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and I want it on the table right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.54,1:27:32.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- OK.  - OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.71,1:27:35.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get  the memos we sent last week?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.01,1:27:39.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,John and I strongly agree  that the time calls for...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.35,1:27:41.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A goddamn fly,  a goddamn fly in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.25,1:27:43.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jesus Christ.  - John and I both think
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.09,1:27:46.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that the time calls for  a period of benign neglect.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.69,1:27:47.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Benign neglect.  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.99,1:27:50.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that. I like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.63,1:27:54.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know, the pigs in the  media describe us as terrorists.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.30,1:27:58.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrorist is one who  terrorizes and frightens others.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.80,1:28:01.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We the ones getting terrorized.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.54,1:28:03.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we exist in, in peace,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.61,1:28:06.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,when we scared to walk  down the street to the store?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.81,1:28:09.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, there's this whole black  power movement going on, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.35,1:28:12.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right.  - What if we, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.39,1:28:18.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Nixon promotes black power
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.66,1:28:22.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to mean "black businesses"  and we find ways to support
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.73,1:28:26.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,black entrepreneurs, pass the buck  on desegregation to the courts.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.26,1:28:28.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Push black enterprise
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.97,1:28:30.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to win the 2O percent  of the votes it could swing our way.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.87,1:28:33.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Excellent, sir.  - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.14,1:28:35.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know if your ceiling gonna  cave in 'cause your slum lord
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.47,1:28:38.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,too busy running around  collecting rent checks.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.14,1:28:40.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But he won't fix your roof.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.18,1:28:43.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time we take a stand  against these injustices
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.98,1:28:45.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that have plagued our community.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.65,1:28:49.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They take one of ours,  we taking two of theirs.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.35,1:28:51.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's right.  - It's been time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.15,1:28:54.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to make sure  that Nixon black power
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.09,1:28:56.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't equate Nixon  with the Black Panthers.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.16,1:28:59.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind, man?  Did you read Hoover's last memo on that?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.00,1:29:01.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's my point.  - Goddamn terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.33,1:29:03.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no. I gave him the green light  to gut those sons of bitches.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.93,1:29:05.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good.  - Good. Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.44,1:29:08.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, round 'em all up and  throw 'em down an elevator shaft.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.54,1:29:15.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't proclaim to know everything.  But I promise you...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.45,1:29:18.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'll always beware  of the nigger with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.39,1:29:25.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Will there be anything else,  Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.77,1:29:38.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How many kids we got coming  to the breakfast tomorrow morning?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.47,1:29:40.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Got about 25 to 3O coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.60,1:29:43.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-five to 3O kids  will be able to go to school
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.21,1:29:45.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and focus on their lessons.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.31,1:29:47.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause they don't want us  to be able to feed our kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.88,1:29:51.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't want us  to be able to protect ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.99,1:30:00.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.72,1:30:04.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought this was going to be  our community service.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.56,1:30:07.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is community service.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.26,1:30:09.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Someone kills one of ours,  we kill two of theirs?"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.83,1:30:11.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Community protection.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.67,1:30:15.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to kill somebody, Carol?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.97,1:30:19.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I ain't.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.58,1:30:23.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.42,1:30:32.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever love me, baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.98,1:31:00.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today, a day after police  shot it outwith the Black Panthers,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.25,1:31:02.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}killing two of them,  they raided the apartment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.45,1:31:04.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the shooting of 26  Panthers in the past year,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.55,1:31:07.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}may represent a national campaign  by police to wipe out the Panthers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.96,1:31:10.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the criminal reaction  of the occupants in shooting{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.39,1:31:12.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}at announced police officers,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.66,1:31:18.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}emphasizes the extreme viciousness  of the Black Panther Party.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.29,1:31:21.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Party ls a Groovy Thing"]
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.53,1:31:47.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, baby-  - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.30,1:31:49.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Happy birthday.  - Happy birthday to me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.47,1:31:51.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.94,1:31:55.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, this is the present  I want, right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.87,1:31:58.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you want it right here?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.34,1:32:00.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-mm, you know right...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.41,1:32:02.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right here?  - Kids up... Kids down...?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.35,1:32:04.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no kids in the house no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.48,1:32:06.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I made you a birthday cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.38,1:32:08.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I got all the cake  I want right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.52,1:32:10.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.39,1:32:13.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I got some champagne  cooling in the icebox.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.39,1:32:15.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And some ice cream, too.  Get some ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.36,1:32:17.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna be drinking with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.19,1:32:20.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.20,1:32:22.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.20,1:32:23.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just playing with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.70,1:32:26.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see you move  a little bit. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.24,1:32:31.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}'{\i0} 9h, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.35,1:32:40.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We get any mail  from Charlie today?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.45,1:32:43.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.62,1:32:46.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- No?  - Haven't heard from Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.49,1:32:48.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.59,1:32:50.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should go  to Shantay's tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.86,1:32:53.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.  No, I'm too old for disco.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.10,1:32:54.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We not old. Come on. We ain't old.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.43,1:32:56.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't feel like  doing no disco.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.33,1:32:58.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boys are gone.  It's just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.23,1:33:02.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You and me, we are free.  I forgot this. I forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.44,1:33:09.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, look at us.  Little happy birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.01,1:33:11.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to go put it on, upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.95,1:33:14.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Put it on?  - Yeah. Go put it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.05,1:33:15.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right.  - Make it snappy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.95,1:33:18.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring down my sewing kit,  'cause I need to do some alterations.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.36,1:33:25.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it snappy!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.56,1:33:31.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.90,1:33:35.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.81,1:33:38.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.71,1:33:41.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You should call me back,  because this is not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.04,1:33:44.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's home again.  - It fit!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.31,1:33:45.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- We gonna go on out tonight.  - Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.98,1:33:48.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's home and...  - Boy, you good, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.08,1:33:50.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You all right?  - Who that?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.92,1:33:53.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me back.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.16,1:33:55.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- OK?  - Oh, it's Louis.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.19,1:33:57.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He asking for some money?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.33,1:34:01.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Louis.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.33,1:34:04.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to hear  from you on my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.30,1:34:07.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You should feel  ashamed of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.40,1:34:10.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a grown-ass man calling  your mama, asking for money.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.27,1:34:12.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And guess what?  It's the butler's money.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.98,1:34:14.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Uncle Tom's money.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.68,1:34:17.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And he ain't giving  none out today.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.35,1:34:20.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.49,1:34:25.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.20,1:34:38.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You got the wrong house.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.21,1:34:45.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the wrong house.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.99,1:35:40.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H247EFC&}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.18,1:35:46.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vietnam took my boy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.02,1:35:50.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I didn't understand why we  were there in the first place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.18,1:36:24.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father still alive, Cecil?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.89,1:36:28.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.02,1:36:30.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My father died when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.53,1:36:42.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else that you  would like, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.37,1:36:44.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Come sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.49,1:36:46.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.18,1:37:08.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a lot of talk  of me resigning and...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.27,1:37:11.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...things of that nature,  but I just want you to know
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.40,1:37:13.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,it's never gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.90,1:37:17.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna come out of this thing  stronger than ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.78,1:37:27.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else  that you would like...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.58,1:37:29.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.92,1:37:38.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Louis is here, looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.93,1:37:46.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Got everybody all worried.  - Well, I finished school.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.47,1:37:47.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my master's  in political science.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.85,1:37:50.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.98,1:37:53.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get that education.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.44,1:37:57.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!  Well, I'm gonna let you all to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.61,1:38:00.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no need for that, Carter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.70,1:38:05.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Dad.  - Get out of here, Louis.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.50,1:38:12.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Dad...  - I said leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.17,1:38:23.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep doing what you doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.43,1:38:29.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Uncle Carter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.77,1:38:34.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you do that? Huh?  That was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.40,1:38:37.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy's hurting, too. He's just  trying to get his act together.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.27,1:38:39.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be hurting, Carter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.49,1:38:43.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy didn't even go  to his own brother's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.45,1:38:49.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's full of shit is what he is.  He ain't doing nothing right.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.49,1:38:52.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He just got his master's!  What more you want him to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.50,1:38:57.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Every gray hair I have  is 'cause of that boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.56,1:39:10.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The years started to drift by,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.81,1:39:14.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the pain in my heart  never went away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.32,1:39:21.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"You and I Ain't Nothin' No More"]
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.57,1:39:28.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Through it all,  Louis and I never spoke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.20,1:39:37.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As we are a nation under God,  so I am sworn...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.27,1:39:58.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Half of our  oil is now imported...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.69,1:40:00.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is a crisis that strikes  at the very hear':{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.90,1:40:03.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and soul and spirit  of our national will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.32,1:40:05.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}I feel one coming now.{\i0}  - {\i1}Not to worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.15,1:40:06.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two of you,  stay home until you feel better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.99,1:40:11.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}OK, Barn, I'll stay.  But I ain't never gonna feel no better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.83,1:40:23.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In our district alone,  we have nine percent unemployment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.84,1:40:26.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the country at large, 14 percent  are living below the poverty line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.63,1:40:30.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sixty percent of those  are either black or Hispanic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.01,1:40:32.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, if I'm voted to Congress,  reducing those figures is gonna be{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.85,1:40:36.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,one of my primary objectives.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.52,1:40:41.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.19,1:40:43.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.11,1:40:45.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for getting back to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.99,1:40:51.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How much did he lose by?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.54,1:40:56.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.79,1:40:58.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.58,1:41:00.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.34,1:41:07.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he didn't win.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.13,1:41:11.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should call him.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.68,1:41:16.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after Charlie passed,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.85,1:41:19.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Louis came over  and paid me a visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.52,1:41:21.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.73,1:41:26.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He found me on the kitchen floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.32,1:41:28.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I had passed out.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.74,1:41:30.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Drunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.91,1:41:35.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd gone to the bathroom  all over myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.75,1:41:40.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one that cleaned me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.46,1:41:47.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And then he told me  I was the best mother
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.59,1:41:50.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,anybody could ever want.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.68,1:41:56.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think, about now...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.77,1:42:01.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...he'd want to hear from his daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.56,1:42:05.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you ought to call him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.65,1:42:11.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.49,1:42:12.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.95,1:42:16.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.12,1:42:19.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.04,1:42:21.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay there, I'm coming to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.04,1:42:24.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I... have a...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.75,1:42:27.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...secret mission for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.55,1:42:29.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.01,1:42:31.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I like to send people  money when they write me
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.47,1:42:33.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,about their financial problems,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.80,1:42:37.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but my staff has been  trying to get me to stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.97,1:42:41.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you could  help me to keep this going?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.89,1:42:44.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.81,1:42:47.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I appreciate  your help with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.57,1:42:50.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And, please, don't tell Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.44,1:42:52.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.03,1:42:59.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Morning, Cecil.  - Morning, Mr. Warner.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.54,1:43:05.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,May I sit down?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.01,1:43:17.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here  for over 2O years now.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.35,1:43:25.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,For all that time,  the black help
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.35,1:43:30.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,has been paid a smaller salary  than the white help.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.61,1:43:35.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just don't think  that's right, Mr. Warner.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.37,1:43:43.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There are black housemen  who should be engineers by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.37,1:43:47.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They should've been promoted  years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.00,1:43:52.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.67,1:44:00.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have to be paid  the same as the white help,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.51,1:44:04.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,or I'm gonna have to move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.48,1:44:08.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you'll be moving on then.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.07,1:44:15.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I told the president  that you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.16,1:44:22.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to tell you  to take this up with him, personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.37,1:44:28.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.47,1:44:39.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not comfortable  with all the foreign policy hawks
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.18,1:44:40.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,surrounding Ronnie, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.89,1:44:45.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We need more moderates on his staff.  And a summit with the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.22,1:44:47.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ronnie has to meet  with them face to face
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.56,1:44:49.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,if we're ever  going to thaw this ice.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.06,1:44:51.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Cecil.  - Yes, Mrs. Reagan?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.73,1:44:54.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We will talk, Jim. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.57,1:44:56.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.40,1:44:58.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very popular around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.82,1:45:03.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone says you're the man  that got them raises and promotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.41,1:45:07.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I had no idea.  - I wish I could take credit for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.87,1:45:10.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to invite you  to the State Dinner next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.63,1:45:13.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm gonna be there, Mrs. Reagan.  - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.17,1:45:18.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as a... Not as a butler, Cecil.  I'm inviting you as a guest.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.88,1:45:22.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But the president prefers  for me to serve him personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.05,1:45:26.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry about, Ronnie.  I'll take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.97,1:45:30.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll see you next week.  You and your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.81,1:45:33.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My Wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.65,1:45:38.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... It's Gloria, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.78,1:45:41.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, ma'am.  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.45,1:45:45.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.63,1:45:59.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the Entrance Hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.80,1:46:06.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.78,1:46:23.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get you a glass  of champagne, Mr. Gaines?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.57,1:46:27.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shut up.  - Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.41,1:46:31.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.21,1:46:35.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the President and First Lady  of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.98,1:46:59.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was different sitting  at the table instead of serving it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.86,1:47:01.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Real different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.70,1:47:07.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could see the two faces  the butlers wore to survive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.79,1:47:13.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I knew I'd lived my life  with those same two faces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.63,1:47:25.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gloria looked so happy,  but I didn't feel the same way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.05,1:47:29.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I wished we were there  for real instead of for show.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.40,1:47:42.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's bon appetit, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.15,1:47:44.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You black mother...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.49,1:47:54.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make myself clear  on this issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.50,1:48:02.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If Congress passes sanctions  against South Africa,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.09,1:48:06.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be forced to  veto those sanctions.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.55,1:48:10.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mr. President, we feel  that that would be a major mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.89,1:48:14.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The brutal repression  of South African black citizens
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.77,1:48:17.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,makes this no longer  a foreign policy issue,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.73,1:48:21.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but a United States racial issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.48,1:48:24.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We're senators  from your own party.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.40,1:48:26.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we feel so comfortable  in letting you know
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.53,1:48:29.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that South Africa  is a human rights disaster.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.74,1:48:33.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Black people are  being beaten, tortured,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.45,1:48:35.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,gunned down  in the middle of the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.62,1:48:39.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Americans see all this on TV,  they're horrified by apartheid.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.54,1:48:42.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.42,1:48:47.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President, your reputation  as a world leader is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.05,1:48:49.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,United States of America needs to be
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.59,1:48:51.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,on the right side of history  on the race issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.93,1:48:54.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I say again.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.93,1:48:59.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If Congress passes this bill,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.02,1:49:01.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I Will veto it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.86,1:49:04.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Peﬂod.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.99,1:49:17.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You reading now?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.00,1:49:19.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up and do the dishes  'fore I shoot your little ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.26,1:49:37.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing seemed right to me  after that State Dinner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.27,1:49:39.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Got all confused.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.21,1:50:09.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They had started writing books{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.30,1:50:14.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}about everything Louis  and his friends had done.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.02,1:50:21.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Louis was never a criminal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.23,1:50:28.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was a hero,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.73,1:50:32.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}fighting to save  the soul of our country.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.25,1:50:46.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Would you like a cookie?  - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.25,1:50:48.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Cookies.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.21,1:50:49.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cookie?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.80,1:50:51.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.92,1:50:53.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.55,1:50:55.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cookie?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.48,1:51:15.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had always loved sewing.  But just felt different now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.20,1:51:23.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know that an old man  could feel so lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.58,1:51:25.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how I felt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.67,1:51:29.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how I felt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.34,1:51:37.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Americans always turned{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.60,1:51:42.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,a {\i1}blind eye to what we'd done  to our own.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.64,1:51:46.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We look out to the world and judge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.60,1:51:49.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We hear about  the concentration camps,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.73,1:51:54.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but these camps went on  for 200 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.86,1:51:58.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}right here in America.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.84,1:52:12.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Buried my daddy right over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.26,1:52:20.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My mama would've been  right proud of me,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.47,1:52:23.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,being with a man like you's.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.43,1:52:27.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking such good care of me  all of these years.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.77,1:52:32.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Cecil Gaines.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.36,1:52:37.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you more, Gloria.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.17,1:52:52.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.75,1:52:54.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.67,1:52:59.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to be the one  to tell you first, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.68,1:53:02.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the best butler here.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.43,1:53:05.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're like family, Cecil.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.89,1:53:09.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Been an honor serving you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.65,1:53:14.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not just for me,  I'm sure I speak for all the presidents
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.02,1:53:18.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,when I say that you've  served your country well.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.49,1:53:22.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.16,1:53:29.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.75,1:53:33.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole civil rights issue...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.01,1:53:40.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes fear I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.30,1:53:43.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,on the wrong side of it,  that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.97,1:53:46.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...just wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.22,1:53:50.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I think I'm just  scared of what it really means.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.44,1:53:55.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm trying not to be  so scared anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.07,1:53:58.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}Who do we want to free?!{\i0}  {\i1}- Mandela!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.86,1:54:00.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When do we want him free?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.24,1:54:01.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Now!  - Free Mandela!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.74,1:54:06.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years ago, we marched  in this country for our rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.41,1:54:12.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we march to free  the people of South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.50,1:54:14.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.04,1:54:18.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ronald Reagan has attacked or dismantled  every civil rights program
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.76,1:54:20.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that has ever been put in place.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.93,1:54:22.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah!  - Right!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.47,1:54:26.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiding the oppression of black South  Africans is absolutely consistent
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.31,1:54:29.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,with his policies on race issues.  Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.98,1:54:32.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Am I right?  - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.40,1:54:36.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.78,1:54:40.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Steven?  Where's Steven?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.69,1:54:42.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Free Mandela!  - Free Mandela, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.70,1:54:45.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Free Mandela!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.28,1:54:51.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Free Mandela!  Free Mandela! Free Mandela!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.63,1:55:04.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.05,1:55:06.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Louis.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.14,1:55:11.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.56,1:55:19.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to protest with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.40,1:55:25.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get arrested, Dad.  You'll lose your job.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.32,1:55:29.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.33,1:55:35.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.34,1:55:48.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.41,1:56:11.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Dad, we'll be  out of here in a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.29,1:56:13.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was worried?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.25,1:56:23.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After going to jail,  I thought I'd seen it all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.05,1:56:26.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You OK, Daddy?  - Yeah, no, no, no. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.97,1:56:30.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I never imagined I'd see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.60,1:56:32.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a black man{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.85,1:56:38.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}be a real contender for  the President of the United States.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.15,1:56:44.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.36,1:56:48.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's that sweet corn.  - That corn look good.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.09,1:57:04.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gloria and I would walk  to our polling place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.38,1:57:09.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}every night to see where  we'd be voting for Barack Obama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.10,1:57:15.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'd just... stare at it, smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.06,1:57:24.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You done?  - Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.27,1:57:26.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.99,1:57:30.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You done pretty good there.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.86,1:57:33.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.12,1:57:38.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How come Louis' wife  named that child...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.33,1:57:41.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...Shaquanda?  - Now, don't start that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.33,1:57:45.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't starting it, I just don't know  what kind of name that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.75,1:57:49.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, really! Shaquanda?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.43,1:57:51.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she done that just to spite me.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.59,1:57:55.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't nobody  done nothing to spite you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.51,1:57:57.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she did.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.23,1:58:02.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,She a ugly little old girl, too.  That little pug nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.98,1:58:07.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I hope she grow out of it.  - Now, you need to stop that.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.23,1:58:09.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You know that ain't right.  - Don't you think
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.28,1:58:11.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,she look a little like  Louis around the mouth?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.32,1:58:15.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think... she look just like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.45,1:58:17.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Like me?  - Yeah, so you need to...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.45,1:58:20.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...you need  to stop talking about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.37,1:58:23.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me look at her again,  then, real good.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:23.54,1:58:25.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Paughs]
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.84,1:58:31.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,She do look a little bit like me.  She a pretty little thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.43,1:58:35.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can put up  with the name Shaquanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.85,1:58:40.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot where I put my Bible.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.10,1:58:43.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You know I need my Bible.  - Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.98,1:58:48.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I think I left it in the bathroom.  - Why is Louis late?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.98,1:58:52.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy gets elected to Congress...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.07,1:58:55.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he ain't been on time  getting us to church ever since.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.62,1:58:59.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can't believe you still... fussing.  - He gonna be late to his own funeral.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.75,1:59:01.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still fussing  about Louis?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.58,1:59:04.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he's gonna be here for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.46,1:59:08.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go ahead, call him.  - I ain't calling Louis.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.80,1:59:12.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get my purse and...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.89,1:59:19.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say? Isaiah?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.35,1:59:23.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you got... your mark here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.73,1:59:27.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fall all over myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.02,1:59:30.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, you need...  to move that to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.33,1:59:45.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.88,1:59:50.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.84,1:59:54.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.39,2:00:00.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.35,2:00:04.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.59,2:00:31.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...states will be closing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.63,2:00:33.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and there are some big ones,  especially California,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.88,2:00:36.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the largest state  in the United States,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.05,2:00:37.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with 55 electoral votes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.84,2:00:40.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hawaii, that's where  Barack Obama was born.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.80,2:00:42.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will be closing its polls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.68,2:00:46.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Idaho, Oregon  and Washington state,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.10,2:00:48.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and those states  have been going Democratic{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.40,2:00:50.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in presidential contests  in recent years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.69,2:00:52.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So in a few seconds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.32,2:00:54.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}those states  will be closing their polls,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:54.61,2:00:57.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and presumably we'll  be able to see what's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.36,2:00:59.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Louis!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:59.36,2:01:01.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a major projection at that point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.37,2:01:04.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a moment that a lot of  people have been waiting for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.75,2:01:07.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Louis, come on down!  Come down!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.37,2:01:09.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...could be rather historic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.29,2:01:15.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And CNN can now project  that Barack Obama, 47 years old,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:15.01,2:01:17.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will become the President-Elect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.63,2:01:20.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}of the United States. We project...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.89,2:01:24.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If there is anyone out there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.26,2:01:28.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who still doubts that America  is a place where{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.39,2:01:30.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}all things are possible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.52,2:01:38.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...who still wonders if the dream of our  founders is alive in our time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.07,2:01:42.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who still questions  the power of our democracy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.32,2:01:45.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tonight is your answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.02,2:02:53.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must look  through their eyes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.11,2:02:57.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...see what it is that they want...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:59.28,2:03:02.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...see what it is that they need...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.91,2:03:06.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...anticipate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.95,2:03:13.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...bring a smile  to the principal's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:21.47,2:03:23.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gaines.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.34,2:03:26.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Admiral Rochon, the chief usher.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.93,2:03:37.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nice to meet you, admiral.  - Pleasure's all mine, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.03,2:03:43.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to tell you  what an honor it is to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.49,2:03:46.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The honor is mine.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.20,2:03:49.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The president's so excited  to meet with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:50.12,2:03:52.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.71,2:03:57.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that's just fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.38,2:03:59.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show  you the way.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.38,2:04:01.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the way.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.68,2:04:07.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heart of the question is,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.68,2:04:11.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}whether all Americans  are to be afforded equal rights{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.01,2:04:13.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and equal opportunities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.85,2:04:20.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is the effort of American  Negroes to secure for themselves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.40,2:04:25.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the full blessings of American life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.15,2:04:27.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will respond  with that timeless creed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.37,2:04:32.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, we can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.99,2:04:45.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H247EFC&}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:45.13,2:04:50.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll Close My Eyes"]

Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:01:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻译： @塔拉Tala
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前只知道一件事，那就是棉花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一项非常辛苦的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此时，当棉铃裂开时就意味着棉花已经成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棉球是星形的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同是镶嵌在夜空中一颗古老的星星.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者就像是你的大脑袋.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等, 那是棉花吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个棉花吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我从不在意,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我可以一整天都和爸爸在一起干活儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:02:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快点, 拍张照片.  - 为你们所有人拍张照片.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都那么严肃?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露出牙齿.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈蒂, 过来  到小屋里帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸爸，他带妈妈去哪儿?  - 快回去干活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔, 回来这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我, 孩子.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟那个男人争论.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他的地盘儿  我们只是住在这里而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听明白了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，现在快回去干活儿吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，你准备怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，上帝呀.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看谁呢?! 啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁不想活了?!  回去干活儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂, 你. 去找几个人挖个坑把他爸爸给埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我要带你去房子里.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会教你成为一名会做屋内服务的黑鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他来了.  - 好的，夫人.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上菜的时候最好不要出声.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好连呼吸声都不要让我听到.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是对, 夫人.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你待在房间里的时候要形同空气.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在房间里干活儿要比在地里干活舒适得多.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个愚蠢的黑鬼, 要记得从左边开始.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多给我一点儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的年纪一天天在长大，我开始意识到  我一定得在他杀了我之前离开.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但与此同时，我却又害怕离开那里.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我从未离开过那个地方.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈, 我带着爸爸的手表.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，我要走了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那次事件之后，我妈妈开始变得沉默寡言.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她会想念我,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也知道她希望我离开那个地方.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有，尽管安娜贝丝小姐对我的离开  从未讲过只言片语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道她也一样会想念我.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得上帝是有意想要拆散一个家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棉花田以外的世界远远比我想像得还要糟糕许多.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人愿意给我提供工作的机会  更不用说食物和睡觉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何一个白人都有可能随时随地杀掉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不用担心遭受惩罚.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:08:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时的法律不仅不会保护我们.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且....对我们很不利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天我都饥肠辘辘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子，你知道这样做的后果会是什么，对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了，起来.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个窗户的事，我必须得跟老板撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是上帝说我们不应该撒谎.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸和妈妈在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈的精神有点不正常  我爸爸被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你做几个火腿三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后送你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期天的早晨是我们最忙的时间.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要帮手吗?  我知道该如何伺候顾客.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打碎了我们的窗户，还偷了我们的食物,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你还想在这里工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在梅肯的时候,我是个做屋内服务的黑鬼  我做得很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再用黑鬼那个词了，知道了吗，孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是白人的词
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个词充满了敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你爸爸没有教过你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 慢一点.  - 是，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要学会看眼色.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过他们的颜色就能知道他们需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明白了吗?  - 嗯，动作要很轻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的，我明白了.  - 给你.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他们需要什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边请.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预测.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，对不起，女士.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要尽可能地让你的服务对像...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露出微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完美，非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了给我留一些猪肠.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么你那么喜欢猪肠?  - 因为猪肠很好吃.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华盛顿Excelsior酒店的经理昨天正好路过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他给我提供了一份男仆的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定会付你最高的薪水吧，老板?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正琢磨着要不要接受那份工作  我还不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经太老了，现在离开北卡罗来纳州  怕是不太合适
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里待着也很不错.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经向他推荐了你.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在这家酒店，我也才刚刚摸出点门道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不足以去应付所有那些傲慢的白人,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有他们的那些花哨的言辞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔, 我们都有两张面孔:  一张是我们自己的,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一张则是我们给那些白人看的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，你想要在这个世界上立足
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定不能让他们感觉到有威胁.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要学会使用我教过你的那些花哨的言语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北方的那些白人们  他们喜欢傲慢的有色人种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了华盛顿的那份工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我所见过的最漂亮的酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你们经历了从布法罗到华盛顿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此漫长的旅程之后,我希望我为你们准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这两杯酒不会太冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法院有史以来作过的做好的决定  就是延缓了这场乱糟糟的乌龙事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让黑鬼小子和白人女孩们在同一所学校上学  有谁听说过比这更荒唐的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要真发生那样的事，那么接下来的事情  就会是黑人和白人开始通奸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:13:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们, 现在的情形不同了  我们可以发动另一场内战.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔, 你对于黑鬼和白人小孩在同一所学校就读  的事有何看法?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说实话, 詹金斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是太关心美国的政治
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者欧洲的政治.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的确也不应该关心, 塞西尔.  他们都是些罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厄尔·沃伦应该被枪决或者处以绞刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个婊子养的傻X法官居然想要整合我们的学校  （指取消美国学校的种族隔离制度）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想沃伦法官会发现执行这一裁决  将会面临巨大的挑战.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太对了, 塞西尔.你说得太对了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为从未梦想过我会在如此奢华的地方工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从未梦想过我会拥有如此棒的生活.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和格罗瑞亚是在Excelsior酒店  一起工作时认识的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是她在酒店里做女仆,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在，她唯一的工作就是  养育和照顾我们的两个儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很确定他们从不知道棉花田是个什么东东.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要去尿尿.  - 今天不行，别在琢磨花招了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快点把作业写完.  - 路易斯在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他去丢垃圾了.  - 又工作到这么晚?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 值夜班感觉怎么样?  - 比上白班轻松多了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我很想你，亲爱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚不是说你要去尿尿吗，那么快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从洗手间出来的时候要记得洗手，小子.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 早上好.  - 早上好.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨，爸爸.  - 嗨，路易斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还好吗?  - 嗯，我很好.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那很好.  - 儿子被别人杀了的那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她正在四处发表演讲呢.  她叫什么名字来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 玛米 提尔.  - 玛米...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛米 提尔， 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那事儿虽然都已经过去三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可感觉就好像是昨天才发生的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那简直就TMD是一种耻辱  他们对那个男孩子所做的那一切.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只是为了寻找一个白人女人而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把他打个半死,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还把他丢到河里，淹死了他.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死的时候只有14岁，  还没路易斯大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那些疯狂的白人南蛮子.  - 谢谢，妈妈.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起码我们在华盛顿  处境要稍稍好一点，对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对待我们也一样很糟糕.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快过来这里, 查理!  把你的手洗了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯说我们不应该再继续忍受那些白人的欺负了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂.  - 闭嘴.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 注意你的言辞.  - 注意你的言辞.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 这里是盖恩斯家.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，对，稍等, 凯根先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是你老板，爸爸.  - 他打电话来有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每当白人打电话来的时候,  我总是会做最坏的打算.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总是觉得那天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能会被解雇，或者其他的类似的事情.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 请跟我来  - 好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是塞西尔 盖恩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很高兴见到你.  - 我也一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你参与政治活动吗, 盖恩斯先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有，先生.  - 那很好.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在白宫，我们不会容忍任何与政治有关的事情.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是怎么找到我的?  - 我没有找你.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在 Excelsior 酒店的时候曾为R.D.沃纳先生服务过.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他负责整个白宫的运营事务.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你给他留下了很深刻的印象.  - 我不记得了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃纳和我一直在为白宫留意和挖掘  一些比较有潜力的员工.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男仆这个职位很少会空缺,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为大部分男仆都会在这个职位上  待30年甚至更久.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接到电话的时候非常惊讶.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得很惊讶.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为白宫的总管,  男仆这个职位通常是由我来负责招聘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法洛斯先生，原谅我这么说...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果雇佣我会让你觉得不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也不想在这种情况下接受这份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要一名你精心挑选的男仆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个各方面都能让你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,称心如意的员工.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是... 路易十三?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些酒瓶是在雅尔纳克战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到的那些金属酒壶的复制品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意大利人很懂他们的葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至于爱尔兰人, 他们也非常明白  如何才能酿制出上好的威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我相信法国人在酿制干邑白兰地方面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有着独特的优势
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说得对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，你会成为一名很好的黑鬼仆人.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要来杯咖啡?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我和法耶会待在这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我，法耶，还有一点点威士忌.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你玩得愉快.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你总是做的很棒.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道如何成功地举办一场舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个土豆沙拉你是怎么弄的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来告诉你我是怎么做的吧  我在沙拉里放了一点小茴香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我在妇女日报上看到的  上面说酸黄瓜会盖掉其他味儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而茴香则会提味儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你现在吃的就是那个加了茴香的东东  - 好吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我很喜欢.  - 跟以前有点点区别，对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真是那么回事.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔肯定让你感到特别骄傲吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，他是靠自己的本事赢得了那份工作  是白宫打电话来找的他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 而不是他打过电话给白宫.  - 他是个很好的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你嫁了个好男人.  - 她很开心呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不像是坐在这里的这位坏脾气的唠叨婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还在生我的气吗?  - 我生气是有原因的.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你没理由生气啦，我已经跟你讲了  我去了那个玩纸牌的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩了会儿牌, 吃了点烧烤,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后，我又去了...  我真的什么都没喝!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很烦... 我很烦再听你说什么打牌的故事，霍华德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎能指望我还会相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你信，或者不信  事实就摆在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好啦，别再吵了  - 你真的想现在吵架么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行啦，你们俩个, 行啦，行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱信不信，你也用不着相信  但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 行啦，你们两个.  - 大骗子.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你真的想挑这个时候吵架么?  - 都马上给我闭嘴.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你总得找个个头和你差不多的人比划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里是为了庆祝塞西尔的新工作的,  所以你们两个能不能好好的哪怕就这一次也行.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到她说的话了吧  来吧，过来让我们庆祝庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是为什么我要出去的原因  我是为了让你开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们俩需要找个房间吧.  - 什么，什么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他都快把我逼疯了.  他... !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你, 嗯... 你想跟我们一起进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂，其他孩子在哪儿?  - 他们在楼上后面的房间.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子们，下来这里吧!  让我看看你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们在上面干嘛呢?  - 祝贺你.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的,你打算什么时候带我去白宫瞧瞧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想去白宫, 宝贝?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我想去白宫.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你想什么时候去?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别跟我瞎逗了...  - 你想什么时候去?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宫,那可是一个很大的进步.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哇!  - 对，让我很兴奋.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘们，大家都去楼上吧!  我想听听所有的故事.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不晓得你究竟想听多少故事,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们已经让他宣过誓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他什么都不能跟我透漏.  - 不会的，姑娘，只要你把他服侍好.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他会告诉你一切的.  - 这就是关键.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你听到她说什么了吗?  - 那你都服侍谁来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛，如果你一直待在家里  我服侍的那个人必然就是你.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你们在说什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子们，你们最好把你们的瘦屁股挪到楼下来!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们来了.  - 都叫你们800遍了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子们，别在房间里四处乱窜.  你们懂的.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔罗伊! 过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我点儿钱.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们... 告诉他们等你长大了你准备干什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要跟盖恩斯先生一样在白宫工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢，那才是我儿子.  - 对.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯! 等你长大了你想干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也想像你爸爸一样在白宫工作吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不知道.  - 我跟你说一件事吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我13岁的时候我就已经非常确切地知道了我的理想.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对, 要做一个赌棍.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是塞西尔 盖恩斯  我是新来的男仆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有16位全职的女仆.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有六位男仆  四位是木匠，两位是油漆匠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七位电工,三位洗碗工, 三位门卫,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位全职的厨房职工，兼任糕点师傅  还有三位全职的誊写员.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.53,0:22:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位油漆匠, 七位电工, 九位机修工...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃纳来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃纳先生, 我想谢谢你给我这个..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:23:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在白宫工作的机会...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，我们走吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人，我是塞西尔 盖恩斯  我会在这里与您一起工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖恩斯先生,请不要那么做.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 走吧.  - 是的，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,端盘子的时候一定要小心不要刮花盘子点底部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不要留意他们的谈话或者作出任何反应
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你待在房间里的时候...  - 要做到形同空气.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他们说...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他们说, "伸出来... "
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"好 "
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后她开始尖叫,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"把你的整个手伸进去!"  所以我就把整个手伸进去.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后她又开始大叫,  "要用两只手!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"好的!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后她又叫, "现在，拍手!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说, "我不能. "
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她仰起头，笑着说,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:24:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"你瞧, 我跟你说了我的... "
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一点儿都不好笑.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.87,0:24:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，他在这里!  我听说你要来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你叫什么名字?  - 塞西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 塞西尔 盖恩斯  - 那不好笑.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.24,0:24:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡特 威尔逊，这里的首席男仆.  别担心你身后的那个大块头.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那哥们会趁你不注意到时候偷走你的钱包.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从镜子里可以看到的那哥们  他叫詹姆斯 霍洛威
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他是我的第二把手.  - 詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.78,0:24:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是杰克 罗宾森还是威利 梅斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.82,0:24:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不能在开始问你那些刁钻问题之前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.19,0:24:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先跟这哥们握个手?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想知道他是打哪儿来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去还没有得出结论，对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.76,0:24:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你. 范希 弗雷迪已经带你参观过了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.16,0:24:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的. 道奇还是...  在输?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.47,0:24:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果卡特能在这里让他闭上他的大嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.97,0:24:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者我能回答你的那个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.67,0:24:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别扯淡了，我们去干活儿吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.26,0:25:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 准备.  - 上帝保佑我们吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.48,0:25:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧张. 放轻松点，去吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.39,0:25:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做到充耳不闻, 视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.56,0:25:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要专心做好你的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.51,0:25:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要派联邦军队去小岩城?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.98,0:25:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真要是到了那一步，那么是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.09,0:26:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不到有任何能让我派联邦军队去南部的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.59,0:26:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从没有.而且那会引发另一场内战.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.93,0:26:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生, 如果联邦政府都无法实施布朗案的裁决  那么还有谁可以呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.87,0:26:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南部一定要遵守联邦法律.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.67,0:26:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只是需要一点时间去适应而已
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.51,0:26:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白, 总统先生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.54,0:26:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果福伯斯继续隔离黑鬼小孩  那我们要怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.68,0:26:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须要执行宪法的规定.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.21,0:26:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多给福伯斯一点时间吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.72,0:26:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有，再劝劝他  相信他会作出让步的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.55,0:26:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是不想太急功近利.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.43,0:26:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么样?  - 我都快尿裤子了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.87,0:26:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前约会过一个女孩  每次我揍她的时候她都会尿自己一身
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.24,0:26:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么?  - 不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.81,0:26:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 闭嘴.  - 你闭嘴吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.01,0:26:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放了一个毛巾在下面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.35,0:27:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，我昨晚送马塞拉睡觉前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.81,0:27:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也说到了相同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.72,0:27:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哇噢，你送她...  - 就像我对待埃迪一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.09,0:27:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做得非常快.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.33,0:27:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你瞧你!  - 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.17,0:27:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌... 沙发上到处都是爆米花
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.61,0:27:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸会杀了...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.34,0:27:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.54,0:27:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨，盖恩斯先生.  - 嗨，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.91,0:27:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，埃尔罗伊.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.35,0:27:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯, 我跟你说过  要让那两个孩子们看其他的电视节目
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.79,0:27:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个电影太恐怖了.  他们的年纪不适合看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.15,0:27:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关掉吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.49,0:27:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要做的就是要笑得甜美一点
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.13,0:27:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让会让男人就会忘记一切
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.79,0:27:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.53,0:27:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格罗瑞亚小姐想要熬夜来着，但是她睡着了.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.30,0:27:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔罗伊, 没人问你话.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.30,0:27:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你妈妈来这里收拾我们大家之前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.14,0:27:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快点轱辘回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.44,0:27:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 得了，爸爸.  - 快走吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.74,0:27:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 拜.  - 把电视关掉.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.95,0:28:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上楼梯的时候轻一点  别吵醒你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.69,0:28:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.33,0:28:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是玛米 提尔的照片?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.40,0:28:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我想要参与这事儿.  - 绝对不行.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.74,0:28:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.91,0:28:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那事儿不会带给你任何好处的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.41,0:28:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，你听到妈妈是怎么说的?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.51,0:28:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些破事儿是发生在南部
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.78,0:28:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但那个人也有可能就是我.  - 那是南部的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.72,0:28:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因为我离开了那里  所以我们才能今天更好的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.02,0:28:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼下我在为白人工作  我只是为了让事情对我们更有利.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.19,0:28:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不是所有的白人都那样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.09,0:28:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把灯关掉. 上床睡觉.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.24,0:29:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你炖了点鸡汤,总统先生
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.45,0:29:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先放在桌子上吧, 塞西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.28,0:29:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.22,0:29:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有把学上完, 塞西尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.62,0:29:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有上过学,总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.43,0:29:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在棉花农场里长大的.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.80,0:29:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是在农场里长大的.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.30,0:29:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有孩子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.70,0:29:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，先生，我有两个儿子.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.70,0:29:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是在综合学校上学的吗?  （非种族隔离学校）
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.81,0:29:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.45,0:29:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.28,0:29:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地方警卫队又把有色人种的孩子们挡在外边.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.42,0:29:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福伯斯跟我保证过那些警卫会护送孩子们进去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.35,0:29:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可见阿肯色州的州长在撒谎  总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.72,0:30:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟有什么毛病?  为什么他非得逼我这么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.80,0:30:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.30,0:30:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的下一步行动必须要大胆而且迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.81,0:30:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我将签发一项总统命令
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.44,0:30:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要发挥联邦军队的效用
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.78,0:30:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以确保联邦法令能在...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.59,0:30:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿肯色州小岩城顺利施行.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.32,0:30:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是必须的..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.29,0:30:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统派遣了军队前往小岩石城
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.19,0:30:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我第一次见到一位白人  为了我们黑人的权益而承担风险
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.30,0:30:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉路易斯  总统正在为我们争取更好的生活.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.60,0:30:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕业典礼总是那么漫长  她还哔哔个没完没了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.24,0:30:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去做点儿土豆沙拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.34,0:30:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在他可以看到我所指的究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.81,0:30:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那太美妙了  我真为你感到骄傲.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.18,0:30:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢，妈妈.  - 那个帽子看起来好傻.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.02,0:31:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸才看起来好傻呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.66,0:31:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我也为你感到骄傲.  - 爸爸，你有没有看到...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.13,0:31:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再在这里瞎嚷嚷了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.36,0:31:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有在我的学校里看到任何白人孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.01,0:31:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么路易斯就看不到总统为了我们所做的努力W?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.38,0:31:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢.  - 要点饼干吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.08,0:31:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要点饼干吗  - 谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.85,0:31:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.26,0:31:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说了我们会迟到的!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.23,0:31:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可不能错过这趟巴士!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.00,0:31:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢，仁慈的上帝呀  - 等一下，稍等.....
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.07,0:31:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么了?  - 我们必须得先说再见.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.87,0:31:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴士是可以等的.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.17,0:31:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西州离这里很远.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.48,0:32:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费斯克可是一所很棒的大学.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.98,0:32:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以去霍华德大学.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.58,0:32:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我简直不敢相信，都这会儿了  你居然还在扯什么霍华德大学
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.39,0:32:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他要去费斯克大学.  - 我知道，我知道，只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.49,0:32:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得离家太远了而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.06,0:32:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那就是重点所在.  - 什么重点?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.13,0:32:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我支烟吧，而且可别跟我说你不抽烟.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.87,0:32:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没烟.  - 过来.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.67,0:32:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你很想哭，是吧，傻瓜.  - 我又不是为你哭.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.47,0:32:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家后看一下你的床垫下面有什么.  我给你留了点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.54,0:32:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他在南方我就无法保护他了.  - 南方已经跟过去不一样了，塞西尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.28,0:32:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还不到看“花花公子”的年纪呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.72,0:32:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里已经不再是你曾经待过的那个南部了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，路易斯把他的色情杂志留给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.05,0:32:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别跟你兄弟瞎说.  - 为什么你要扇他呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.06,0:32:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他才是拿着杂志的那个人.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.82,0:32:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我爱你，妈妈  - 我也爱你，儿子.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.26,0:32:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我爱你，路易斯  - 我也爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.33,0:32:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我给你做了火腿三明治  - 谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.33,0:32:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.84,0:33:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.35,0:33:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.68,0:33:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.25,0:33:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很为你骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.86,0:33:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.30,0:33:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.67,0:33:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有什么需要，就打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.41,0:33:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的.  - 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.38,0:33:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜 妈妈.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.12,0:33:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜 路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.83,0:33:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.57,0:34:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请再提醒我一下为什么我们要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.74,0:34:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人能告诉我吗  那玩意看上去就像是一个苦瓜脸
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.74,0:34:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看起来就是那样  - 那是法国的烘培艺术.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.35,0:34:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了吧，黑鬼.  别跟我扯什么"法国的烘培艺术 "
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.78,0:34:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这很明显狗屁都不是.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.02,0:34:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不...  - 男孩子的头脑总是那么简单.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.79,0:34:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我玩给你看吗?  我来玩给你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.82,0:34:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.73,0:34:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这会很好看，如果再给它弄个小...  弄个小乳头在上面.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.76,0:34:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了，哥们.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.20,0:34:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不就是这么玩的吗.  你摇晃它. 你摆弄它.....
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.40,0:34:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个傻子.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.87,0:34:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好, 副总统先生
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.74,0:34:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那看上去很美味呀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.61,0:34:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，先生
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.71,0:34:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你们大家带了点东西来.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.65,0:34:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，副总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.15,0:34:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想说任何不利于那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.05,0:34:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼迪男孩的事儿.  我很肯定他是个很友善的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.42,0:35:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你们真的想让那个被宠坏的...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.53,0:35:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,富人家的婊子养的家伙...  成为你们的下一任总统吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.67,0:35:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.07,0:35:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会为你加油的，副总统先生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.97,0:35:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，塞西尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.88,0:35:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我来问你点儿事儿吧  坦率的说,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.55,0:35:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为黑人社区的成员  你最关心的事情是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.79,0:35:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说说看，小伙子们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.89,0:35:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别不好意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.76,0:35:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍洛维，你说说
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.60,0:35:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧，因为你问到了，先生...  - 对，我在问你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.44,0:35:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样的活儿，支付给有色员工的薪水  比支付给白人的薪水要低40%
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.57,0:35:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是这样吗?  - 是的，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.78,0:35:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且有色员工基本没有升迁的机会.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.12,0:35:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你吧，如果我是总统  我会为你们加薪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.29,0:36:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且让你们都得到升职.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.19,0:36:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那.. 那会很棒，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.46,0:36:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我向你保证.  - 谢谢你，先生
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.43,0:36:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在，你要让你们的人为我投票
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.33,0:36:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我说的那一切将会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.70,0:36:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那个分给大家.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.06,0:36:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是什么意思，你不想跟任何人约会?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.16,0:36:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是有那么多人在追你.....
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.50,0:36:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我只是...  - 比如那一位?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.07,0:36:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在说的是你和艾萨克.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.04,0:36:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦，告诉我发生什么事了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.50,0:36:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩看起来很开心.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.31,0:36:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧，我都没法跟你正常说话，因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.08,0:37:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂.  - 你在寻找真爱的吗, 帅哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.36,0:37:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是为什么我要把  劳森研讨会称为爱之学校的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.66,0:37:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那就是你正在寻找的吗?  - 那就是我来费斯克大学的原因.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.23,0:37:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.40,0:37:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是卡罗尔 阿米耶.  - 罗伊斯 盖恩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.94,0:37:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，跟着我.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.21,0:37:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个乡下男孩, 是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.51,0:37:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是一名医生.  你爸爸是做什么的?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.78,0:37:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在政治领域工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.85,0:37:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要没有人帮忙你是很难找到这个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.52,0:37:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...而且你也无法维持超过一个月.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.39,0:37:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的吗?  - 这需要时间, 还需要有承担,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.76,0:37:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要有献身精神, 严格的纪律以及专注的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.36,0:37:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们得衡量我们取得的每一个阶段性的成就，对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.57,0:37:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一个能够投机取巧的事情  过去一周都没有再发生过那样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.93,0:37:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这需要一个我们一直以来  所探讨的严格的纪律
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.34,0:38:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们如何来衡量这些事情呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.31,0:38:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要回头去看看像甘地那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.91,0:38:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要一起去学习甘地的经验和技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.88,0:38:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他在南非和印度的影响力会那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.95,0:38:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论是对于他自己的人民，还是对于其他国家的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.62,0:38:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要借鉴他们的经验，而且要用在纳什维尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.62,0:38:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要组建一支部队.你们和我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.42,0:38:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这支部队只有一种武器  那个武器就是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.43,0:38:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此刻，我就是... 你说.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.33,0:38:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们唯一的武器是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.67,0:38:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他们的武器是真的武器,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.00,0:38:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是说，那不是很危险吗?  - 噢，你会被他们杀掉的.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.67,0:38:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有谁不喜欢我们的主张,  你知道门在哪儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.07,0:38:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白那听起来充满了挑衅，但那是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.98,0:38:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，同学们  现在是演出时间
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.70,0:39:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘地已经向我们证明了  在他们国家或者任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.60,0:39:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生活着的那些棕色人种...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.41,0:39:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...可以不再忍受脱离种族隔离制度的压迫
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.31,0:39:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有无比的耐心、坚持和毅力,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.98,0:39:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,运用自己智慧和思想，以及自律...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.19,0:39:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...还有一点点幽默感.  我们就可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.50,0:39:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道你们是不可以坐在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.53,0:39:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很愿意接受你的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.90,0:39:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们所谈论的事情并不是没有先例
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.74,0:39:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这需要我们有足够的耐心.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.01,0:39:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以去有色人种的那个区域点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.05,0:39:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这里  我不会为你提供服务的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.25,0:39:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是有组织的.  我们每一个团队都设有一名领导.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.88,0:39:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有负责观察和监督的人员
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.59,0:39:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及当地的救护车电话号码
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.42,0:39:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦有人在那个餐馆里遇到麻烦  接下来要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.53,0:40:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他坐在餐馆里的黑人学生
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.36,0:40:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要上前向他们陈述你们的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.50,0:40:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请为我们提供服务，谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.44,0:40:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，有谁愿意参与角色扮演?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.20,0:40:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆，我这里需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.67,0:40:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都知道你们不应该坐在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.68,0:40:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 攻击.  - 站起来，黑鬼，站起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.61,0:40:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是一次试验.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.21,0:40:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，要尽一切可能去挫败对方的锐气
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.55,0:40:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快点，站起来，黑鬼  - 要使用语言.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.82,0:40:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要听到从你们的嘴里说出 "黑鬼" 这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.29,0:40:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我需要听到你们说 "coon. "(也是侮辱黑人的称谓)  - 说那个会让我感到不舒服.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.19,0:40:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你来到这里，就要做好准备  也要让她做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.96,0:40:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，现在说给我听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.03,0:40:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 黑鬼.  - 大声点.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.40,0:40:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要让别人听起来好像你是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.13,0:40:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 黑鬼.  - 大声点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.10,0:40:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个黑鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.40,0:40:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得去坐在有色人种的座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.21,0:40:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是你待的地方  在这里你不会得到服务的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.31,0:40:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该按照这位女士的吩咐  去坐在你该坐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.61,0:40:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是个黑鬼  - 要让她相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.78,0:40:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不相信你  - 你是个黑鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.48,0:40:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道有色人种应该坐在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.78,0:40:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到那边的那些人类吗  他们就坐在他们自己的区域里
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.39,0:41:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你个死黑鬼!  快起来，你个黑鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.92,0:41:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想让我们在这里买东西  那就别让他们待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.23,0:41:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点，罗伯特，我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.58,0:41:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这对黑鬼鸳鸯, 快点出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.58,0:41:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快起来，死猴子，起来!  - 怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.78,0:41:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没听到我们的话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.78,0:41:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里写着"只欢迎白人. "
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.45,0:41:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来，黑鬼, 起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.36,0:41:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有黑鬼在这里呀?  - 你们在这里做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.50,0:41:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 难道这里有写着 "黑鬼?"  - "只欢迎白人. "
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.40,0:41:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不属于这里. 这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.34,0:41:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- D难道这里有写着 "黑鬼?"  啊?  - 你们在这里做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.94,0:41:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 仔细听着.  - 不，只有白人能待在这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.21,0:41:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不属于这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.84,0:42:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在读什么呢?  我还不知道黑鬼也会阅读
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.05,0:42:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么玩意儿, 傻X  你们现在是一对黑鬼鸳鸯了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.75,0:42:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快起来，你个死黑鬼  看着我!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.85,0:42:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看着我!  - 你们在这里做什么??
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.02,0:42:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你个没教养的死猴子?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.19,0:42:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听明白了吗? 明白了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.29,0:42:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手，住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.83,0:42:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你们能在这里干嘛呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.23,0:42:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来，快起来，你个死黑鬼  看着我，看着我!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.73,0:42:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那上边，还是在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.17,0:42:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用不着告诉我,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.64,0:42:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是你必须得做个决定.  - 我是个黑鬼.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.92,0:42:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 滚回你来的地方!  - 给你，你不是想来点咖啡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.01,0:43:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...黑鬼们最好滚回他们自己的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.88,0:43:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是待在白人的学校里.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.38,0:43:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为我们的国家服务.  - 为我们的国家服务.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.02,0:43:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的兄弟.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.23,0:43:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在觉得很富有  我喜欢这个口味.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.52,0:43:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没他们什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.32,0:43:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...最好滚回他们自己的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.92,0:43:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是待在白人的学校里.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.33,0:43:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个都被判定....
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.16,0:44:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 在郡监狱服刑30天.  - 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.77,0:44:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法警, 把这些黑鬼带离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.92,0:44:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里发生了一些很特别的事情，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.03,0:44:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于一个进了监狱的有色人种可言  还能有什么特别的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.17,0:44:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟在拿老子辛辛苦苦赚来的钱  搞虾米灰机?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.84,0:44:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在学校吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.21,0:44:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在试着改变黑鬼的...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.64,0:44:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你违法了法律.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.35,0:44:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个法官刚刚才宣判你去郡教养所服刑30天.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.85,0:44:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.75,0:44:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我都无法坐在任何我想坐的餐馆里,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.35,0:44:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我还不如死了算了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.15,0:44:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们在为我们的权利而奋斗.  - 权利?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.29,0:44:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你究竟是说什么呢?  - 我们在试着改变
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.69,0:45:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家的民众对待黑鬼的态度和意识.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.23,0:45:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你寄给我的那些明信片是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.66,0:45:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你就是该死的谎话精.  - 我一直在学校.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.57,0:45:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你是在跟谁说话呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.67,0:45:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我把你带到了这个世界上  我也一样可以带你离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.94,0:45:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们一直跟他有联络?  - 谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.47,0:45:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 路易斯  - 对
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.61,0:45:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他参加了一个什么东东  叫什么“自由骑士”
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.28,0:45:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不明白那究竟是个什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.98,0:45:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去看他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.55,0:46:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想要去看他
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.72,0:46:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是每次我一提这茬儿  塞西尔就跟我发火
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.99,0:46:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不晓得我究竟什么时候才能去看他
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.12,0:46:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"试着想要.... "  你看，这就是问题所在
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.63,0:46:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想去就去，别老是想来想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.73,0:46:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有没有带你去过白宫?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.40,0:46:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，塞西尔说我们很快就会去了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.24,0:46:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"塞西尔说，塞西尔说. "
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.97,0:46:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都四年了.你还是那么容易就相信他说的话，亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.78,0:46:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白.  我也不明白为什么他就不能....
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.08,0:46:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...让总统干点啥.  - 你看，吉娜，这就是你的问题所在.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.51,0:46:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就知道说这些傻乎乎的屁话
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.92,0:46:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统有那么多的事要做  那里有功夫去理会路易斯的那点愚蠢的破事
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.49,0:46:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你就不能干脆闭上嘴?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.12,0:46:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在遇上这么糟心的事儿  你就不能表现得友好一点吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.63,0:46:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁跟你说了你可以让我闭嘴的?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.76,0:46:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗯... 你..  - 去给我拿点喝的来.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.93,0:46:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要喝点儿苏格兰威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.20,0:46:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我个人的想法是路易斯会  把我们大家都害死的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.18,0:46:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会来抓我们的.  他们会来抓我们的.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.01,0:47:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就跟他妈妈一样疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.51,0:47:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说，在好的方面.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.85,0:47:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起! 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.35,0:47:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来这里啦.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.39,0:47:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是跟这你们进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.53,0:47:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了艾森豪威尔总统的一个电报  上面说...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.10,0:47:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统会住在白宫
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.30,0:47:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直到下一位总统宣誓就职
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.70,0:47:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，在总统的就职典礼进行期间
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.54,0:47:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,员工只有两个小时的时间  要把上一任总统的东西搬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.41,0:47:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后再把新任总统的东西搬进来.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.91,0:47:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说，这个新来的白人小子很圆滑
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.79,0:47:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想快点回家找格罗瑞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.09,0:47:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忙活这半天累得快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.76,0:47:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子怎么样了, 塞西尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.53,0:47:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们, 总统到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.53,0:47:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的  - 我们要从哪儿开始?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.94,0:47:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不确定  也许我们从那边开始?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.57,0:48:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢  - 请这边走，总统先生
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.21,0:48:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 大家好  - 总统先生
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.18,0:48:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能和你们大家一起共事让我很激动
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.48,0:48:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在接下来的四年里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.35,0:48:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是八年，杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.08,0:48:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，你们会看到谁会在这里当家
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.25,0:48:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不一定能记住你们每一位的姓名  但是我会试试看的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.06,0:48:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰西. 你在这里会很好  因为我会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.26,0:48:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你. 这位是罗琳.  - 很荣幸见到你.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.20,0:48:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 总统先生  - 你好，詹姆斯先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.80,0:48:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 卡特.  - 很荣幸见到你，总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.00,0:48:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 卡特.  - 这位是塞西尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.70,0:48:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很荣幸见到你，总统先生.  - 你好?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.33,0:48:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 威廉.  - 肯尼迪夫人.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.64,0:48:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 格雷格.  - 你好?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.74,0:48:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温斯洛.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.07,0:48:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拣起来了，她没事.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.28,0:48:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴见到你，卡罗琳小姐.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.24,0:48:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 迈尔斯.  - 迈尔斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.51,0:48:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的呼吸里是什么味道,  格罗瑞亚? 住手，好吗，住手.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.02,0:48:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是什么?  - 宝贝，那是杜松子酒的味道.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.82,0:48:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我从这里都可以闻得出来  - 那叫作阿狄森氏病
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.82,0:48:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手，住手啦，你能住手嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.29,0:48:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天有没有带查理去看牙医?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.90,0:49:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在白宫有人得了阿狄森氏病?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.43,0:49:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，我今天没有带查理去看牙医.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.40,0:49:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，你问那些做什么?  你又从来不在家.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.37,0:49:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你问这个就好像你会带查理去看牙医一样
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.01,0:49:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从来都不会在家.  我都不知道你要怎么样带他们去
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.11,0:49:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的牙齿脱落了  他等着你带他去看牙医呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.65,0:49:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快睡觉吧，格罗瑞亚  我明天会带他去
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.09,0:49:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她究竟有多少双鞋子呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.36,0:49:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问你呢，杰奎琳·肯尼迪夫人究竟有多少双鞋子呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.46,0:49:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我他妈的怎么知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.54,0:49:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一天到晚都待在白宫里吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.24,0:49:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你无所不知呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.84,0:49:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你就会一进家门  告诉我我应该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.11,0:49:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,担心我是不是喝酒了.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.98,0:49:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔，你应该多操心自己家里的事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.52,0:49:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的儿子还在监狱里呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.15,0:49:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的儿子在监狱里  可你都不能回家
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.13,0:50:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你... 你没看到我正在试着跟你谈话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.33,0:50:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我敢打赌你肯定希望我能说法语  就像杰奎琳一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.00,0:50:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰奎琳 肯尼迪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.64,0:50:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎样, 就怎样.（法语）
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.81,0:50:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.64,0:50:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢她说话的方式吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.88,0:50:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔，你听没听到我在跟你说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.05,0:50:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就没睡着.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.57,0:50:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍比告诉总统说
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.01,0:50:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不应该担心那些黑鬼静坐示威的事
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.81,0:50:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民意调查显示美国的民权问题始终没有得到改善.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.35,0:50:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说过那个白人男孩（总统）很圆滑  依我看来他有点太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.16,0:51:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂，塞西尔，你儿子怎么样了?  - 已经出狱了，他说他已经回去学校了,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.09,0:51:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得他还在从事  他那个什么自由骑士的事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.43,0:51:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格罗瑞亚还在喝酒吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.20,0:51:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在断断续续地喝.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.10,0:51:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说那个家伙的演奏非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.27,0:51:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 帕布罗·卡萨尔斯，在全世界都很有名  - 他当然很有名啦.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.24,0:51:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得肯尼迪夫人会，嗯 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.18,0:51:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让什么不知名的小人物来这里为她演奏小提琴?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.61,0:51:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 得啦.  - 为什么你不整一个乐队?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.15,0:51:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你也可以出去那里演奏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.92,0:51:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗，事实上  我们可以一起组建一个乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.22,0:51:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会弹奏小手鼓.  你准备弹奏什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.16,0:51:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会吹奏长笛  （skin flute也有口交的意思）.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.62,0:51:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- # 巴巴鲁.  - 卡萨尔斯是一个正直的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.30,0:51:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拒绝去任何一个承认佛朗哥政权的国家演奏  （弗朗西斯科佛朗哥是西班牙的独裁领袖）
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.73,0:51:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佛朗哥是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.07,0:51:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 当我没说.  - 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.90,0:51:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我没说，你太无知了.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.59,0:52:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萝尔, 你累了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.65,0:52:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是想让我靠在你肩膀上
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.39,0:52:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么不对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.76,0:52:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会靠在你的肩膀上啦.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.13,0:52:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当然可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.50,0:52:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前从没坐过自由巴士?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.93,0:52:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有，这是我第一次乘坐.  - 没有吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.40,0:52:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你男朋友对此有何看法?  - 我男朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.44,0:52:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我是说  这会惹他不开心吧，对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.31,0:52:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在坐在这辆巴士上.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.14,0:52:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没有男朋友  - 你没男朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.41,0:52:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能没有男朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.98,0:52:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要不要吃点花生?  - 不要了，谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.99,0:52:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你喜欢吃花生还是...?  - 我不喜欢花生.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.62,0:52:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不能吃东西.  - 喂，我可以吃点儿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.42,0:52:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是一次长途旅行.  - 好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.97,0:52:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯，那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.91,0:53:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是一个十字架. 那是一个十字架.  - 司机，转弯，快转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.02,0:53:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，靠.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.72,0:53:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑鬼们，滚出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.39,0:53:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑鬼，滚回家吧, 黑鬼，滚回家吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.61,0:54:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，上帝呀. 大家都出去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.79,0:54:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在巴黎的一所外面盖满了...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.19,0:54:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葡萄藤的老房子里...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.56,0:54:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...住着12位小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.57,0:54:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中最小的那一位叫玛德琳
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.27,0:54:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就像卡罗琳吗.  - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.14,0:54:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一点都不害怕老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.05,0:54:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么人们要乘坐那辆自由巴士呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.85,0:54:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍比叔叔告诉我爸爸说
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.86,0:55:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天有一辆自由巴士爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.70,0:55:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能告诉你我是如何离开那辆巴士的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.00,0:55:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己从车里爬出来的  还是有人拉我出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.64,0:55:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我儿子是否还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.61,0:55:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我从那辆车里出来的时候  一个男人向我走了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.51,0:55:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时我正在剧烈咳嗽，几乎要窒息而死了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.61,0:55:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我听到他说, "孩子，你没事吗?"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.48,0:55:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我点了点头  我所知道的下一件事就是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.98,0:55:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我躺在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.82,0:55:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在用一个棒球棒用力地打我.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.12,0:55:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.69,0:55:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，爸爸.  我现在在密西西比.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.43,0:55:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你在阿拉巴马.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.03,0:55:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那里的监狱里待了两周  现在我们在密西西比.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.47,0:55:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能听我说，路易斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.87,0:55:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能回家
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.24,0:55:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我们对一些事情的看法有分歧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.21,0:55:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你妈妈她，  她很想你能回家
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.92,0:56:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们扣留了我.  - 要多久?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.32,0:56:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他在哪儿?  - 我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.22,0:56:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说大概要三个月.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.09,0:56:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我出去的时候  我会开始另一次自由之旅.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.03,0:56:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在说什么呀?  - 他怎么说?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.16,0:56:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我跟他说，把电话给我.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.90,0:56:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘那辆巴士，那是我的权利  那是我的合法权利
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.83,0:56:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为一名美国公民，我要运用我的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.17,0:56:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国公民.  你说什么呐?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.37,0:56:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他们会如何对待你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.27,0:56:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会将你处以私刑
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.88,0:56:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会把你扔进河里
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.85,0:56:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.42,0:56:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，那么他们起码得杀了我，才能阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.52,0:56:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...伯明翰的黑鬼和白人
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.26,0:56:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在制造类似的此种冲突.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.26,0:56:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的情形非常严峻，几乎要引发一次暴动了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.76,0:56:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方已经拘捕了大量的肇事人员.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.77,0:56:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且所有都因为相同的原因遭到了起诉...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.37,0:56:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你，总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.87,0:56:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会等你签完字.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.74,0:56:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城市警察已经在着手扩大监狱的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.11,0:57:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以备不时之需
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.61,0:57:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们这样做的目的是为了迎合...的意愿...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.21,0:57:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道我现在看到的  这个究竟是什么国家
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.72,0:57:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...这种论调已经持续了许多年
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.37,0:57:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去，出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.38,0:57:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在阿拉巴马州伯明翰市,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.38,0:57:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在这里的人们走上街头  去关注他们为了对抗美国政府
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.88,0:57:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于美国黑人所实施的种族隔离制度所作出的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.75,0:57:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是早些时候发生在伯明翰的  为了向....施压的抵抗示威活动...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.96,0:57:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯，那个小黑鬼可能做了点儿什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.66,0:57:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许再叫他黑鬼,  因为他不是黑鬼.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.07,0:57:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题嘛，宝贝?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.00,0:58:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就是这个问题.  - 你说什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.34,0:58:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是问题所在  那是不对的，那是不对的.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.34,0:58:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们也没有做错什么.  - 我不能这么对待塞西尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.75,0:58:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么做又不是冲着塞西尔  我这么做是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.48,0:58:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能离开我的房子.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.19,0:58:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你觉得为什么上帝  会让我们俩每天都待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.36,0:58:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这跟上帝一点儿关系都没有.  - 是他让你住在了我的隔壁.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.36,0:58:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是总在说塞西尔待在白宫的时候  你有多么多么孤独和寂寞...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.00,0:58:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你需要一个男人能像我一样..
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.50,0:58:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欣赏你，并且感激你所付出的爱...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.94,0:58:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你这快点把你的赌棍屁股挪出我家门
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.67,0:58:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上从我的沙发上起来.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.18,0:58:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我... 我们俩结束了.  我已经告诉你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.88,0:58:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我来证明给你看.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.55,0:58:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再来这里发表你的那些狗屁演说
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.65,0:58:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是那个了.  - 比那个更扯...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.52,0:58:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是你, 对吗?  你正在朝着你的方向前进.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.02,0:58:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你拿我的衣架瞎搞什么呢?  - 这一个是你, 这一个是我.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.72,0:58:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，我们看上去好像完全不合拍  我们只是不小心碰到了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.19,0:58:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是接下来 我们开始慢慢回到了正确的位置上
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.80,0:59:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像上帝安排你住在了我的隔壁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.83,0:59:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事看起来都有了转机.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.27,0:59:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你的热情减退了，我也能明白你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.28,0:59:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬起你的脏屁股，滚出我的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.98,0:59:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们需要彼此  - 我需要的是我的丈夫.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.85,0:59:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是和你待在破贫民窟里
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.43,0:59:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就平均而言，你觉得我一天大概  要吃多少药，塞西尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.90,0:59:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多... 103, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.54,0:59:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 扶我起来.  - 总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.62,0:59:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你儿子是一名自由骑士.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.12,1:00:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此刻他正和马丁.路德.金待在伯明翰的监狱里
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.23,1:00:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.40,1:00:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...你知道他怎么样吗, 先生?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.54,1:00:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他应该被打得够呛  但是根据他的记录来看
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.11,1:00:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定早已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.78,1:00:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔, 过去两年里他已经被逮捕过16次了.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.89,1:00:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.13,1:00:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没事了吗, 先生?  - 就这样吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.53,1:00:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，我以前一直都不明白
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.80,1:00:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们究竟都经历过什么...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.27,1:00:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...直到我看到了那个.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.88,1:00:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我兄弟说那些孩子们...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.15,1:00:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...改变了他的心意.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.49,1:01:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也改变了我的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.49,1:01:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失望和纷争之火在  北部以及南部的每座城市燃烧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.53,1:01:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在南北方没有法律补救措施的地方燃烧。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.40,1:01:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们上街示威、游行、抗议，
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.04,1:01:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此来寻求补救之法....
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.84,1:01:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此，我要求
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.28,1:01:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国会立法
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.31,1:01:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赋予所有美国人在宾馆、
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.35,1:01:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,餐厅、剧场、...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.85,1:01:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零售店以及类似公共场
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.75,1:01:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,享受服务的权利。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.92,1:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这在我看来是一项基本权利.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.36,1:01:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对这项基本权利的剥夺是恣意损害公民尊严的行为
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.83,1:01:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是1963年的美国人不应当被迫容忍的行为  但有许多人却在容忍
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.33,1:01:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一场重大变革的变革即将到来，
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.00,1:01:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我们的任务、我们的义务是使这场革命  这场变革对于所有人都是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.41,1:01:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平的和具有建设性的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.48,1:02:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所作为者是在自取耻辱和鼓励暴力...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.24,1:02:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，塞西尔  塞西尔，怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.04,1:02:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.75,1:02:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.85,1:02:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们打中了他...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.72,1:02:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...的头.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.09,1:02:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你说的是谁呀?  - 肯尼迪.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.04,1:03:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼迪总统被枪击了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.34,1:03:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当他乘车从达拉斯机场前往达拉斯市中心时...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.08,1:03:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们杀了他.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.31,1:03:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他同乘一辆车的时任德州州长康纳利  也同时遭到枪击
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.85,1:03:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据报道称，现场一共有三发子弹
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.55,1:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位前海军陆战队员...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.75,1:03:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们杀死了我们的老大.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.35,1:03:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"他死了. " 他是否与肯尼迪总统有关联
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.59,1:03:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前还不得而知
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.46,1:03:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统倒在她的妻子肯尼迪夫人的怀中
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.93,1:03:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到救护车前来将他们带离现场
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.63,1:03:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往达拉斯城外的帕克兰纪念医院...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.67,1:03:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼迪夫人拒绝更换她的服装
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.50,1:03:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此，所有的人都可以看到  他们对她的丈夫所做的事
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.85,1:03:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最后一次见到那么多的血
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.12,1:03:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在我爸爸被杀害的那一天.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.63,1:04:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我要如何才能帮到你.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.17,1:04:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.71,1:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你，我想让你把这个盒子带到地下室去
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.51,1:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要记得在上面贴上“奖杯”的标签  - 这是路易斯的东西，妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.85,1:04:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你这么做会惹恼他的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.52,1:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不在乎路易斯是不是会被惹恼.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.39,1:04:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我才是被惹恼的那个人  三年来他从未回来过这里
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.69,1:04:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你生什么气呢，妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.39,1:05:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不要把那个东西放在我的秋葵罐子边上
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.22,1:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有人乐意闻那个臭得要命的秋葵呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.03,1:05:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来的时候，帮我带一点新鲜的食物
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.85,1:05:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看总统...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.72,1:05:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...这是肯尼迪夫人送给我的.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.55,1:05:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是属于肯尼迪总统的.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.59,1:05:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格罗瑞亚...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.39,1:05:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统被杀害了.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.63,1:05:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于总统的事，我很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.73,1:05:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很遗憾.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.77,1:05:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你和那个白宫跟我一毛钱关系都没有
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.27,1:05:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不在乎那所房子里发生的事.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.21,1:05:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在乎的是这所房子里发生的事
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.78,1:06:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道格罗瑞亚最近一段时间  一直都很不开心
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.15,1:06:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那也许就是她喝酒的原因
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.36,1:06:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她希望我跟路易斯能相处得更好一点
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.96,1:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不知道应该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.30,1:06:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也做不到
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.83,1:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以减少待在白宫的时间.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.14,1:06:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也尽量在那么做
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.54,1:06:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有多少双鞋子?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.81,1:07:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她大概有... 125双吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.85,1:07:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 125双鞋子?  - 是的.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.51,1:07:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要让黑人和白人之间站成一排
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.59,1:07:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你.下一次如果再让我发现  房间里没人还开着灯
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.36,1:07:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会开除这个房子里的不负责任的婊子养的  我是认真的，塞西尔
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.53,1:07:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有必要的话，我会回去德州从一个肮脏的  小棚屋开始着手管理这个国家
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.83,1:07:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你所希望的吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.36,1:07:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得是谁在这里支付这些该死的账单?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.10,1:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会呢，但是你明白我的意思
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.63,1:07:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.07,1:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，对，我差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.97,1:07:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰逊夫人和我希望你收下这个
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.21,1:07:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很衬你的眼睛.  - 谢谢你，总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.42,1:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很好，格罗瑞亚  - 快点啦 ,宝贝.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.68,1:07:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摇摆两下，格罗瑞亚.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.25,1:07:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我看到你了，宝贝.  - 你看到我了，宝贝, 快穿上.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.83,1:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，格罗瑞亚.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.70,1:07:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那才是我说的嘛.  - 你们做到了，摇起来!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.94,1:08:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑鬼! 滚出这里.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.37,1:08:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我的洗手间弄得臭哄哄的.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.14,1:08:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢，上帝呀  - 噢，上帝呀
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.94,1:08:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.41,1:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇噢!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.55,1:08:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.85,1:08:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你来一点!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.92,1:08:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你知道.  - 那是你的朋友.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.02,1:08:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我的假发还给我!  你有毛病啊?!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.63,1:08:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是我最好的假发!  - 噢，我靠!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.56,1:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 坐下.  - 我们拿到黑桃了（不晓得啥游戏）.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.40,1:08:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥们刚处理完他的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.03,1:08:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他仍然可以来个劈叉  我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.87,1:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯跟我我说，金博士告诉总统...  （马丁.路德.金）
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.24,1:08:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去街上投选票了.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.44,1:08:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是不是你说的，宝贝?  - 什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.31,1:08:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是跟我说了那个金博士告诉总统
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.54,1:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去街上投选票了.?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.75,1:08:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那不是我编造的吧.  - 你真的听他们那么说来着?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.45,1:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个金博士可不会端着他的  那个好斗的小屁股开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.75,1:08:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她他妈的说得多了.  - 听起来好像是某个人在讲话
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.15,1:08:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.42,1:08:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别欺负我的小鸟.  - 你知道有三个孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.06,1:08:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里被杀害了,  所以他们想让黑人去参加投票
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.96,1:08:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是为什么我不想路易斯去那儿的原因
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.46,1:09:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我一直想要告诉你的事
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.06,1:09:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当时就不应该让他去那里
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.53,1:09:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我知道  - 但是现在,他已经在那里了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.77,1:09:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们现在对此也无能为力.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.80,1:09:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统之所以会派遣FBI  唯一原因就是..
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.51,1:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个都是白人.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.87,1:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那又是谁告诉你的?  - 对啊，那是谁告诉她的?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.94,1:09:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我从巴尔的摩的一张黑人报纸上看到的  你满意了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.78,1:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧，她现在变聪明了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.28,1:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的, 你觉得总统是不是应该
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.58,1:09:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就选举权法案做点儿什么?  - 那又不是王牌.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.15,1:09:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰逊总统刚刚从通过了一项..
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.82,1:09:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自林肯总统废除奴隶制以来  最大的民权法案
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.99,1:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在如此短的时间内通过  另外一项法案肯定会非常困难
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.63,1:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就是那么回事  - 你们看到我老婆是如何盘问我的了吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.00,1:09:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我每天都接受这种盘问.  - 但是你必须要知道
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.13,1:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么能说什么不能说...  一定不能越界.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.34,1:09:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你处理好你老婆的事  我来处理我老婆的事
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.04,1:09:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最起码你会告诉你老婆  那里究竟发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.24,1:09:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 靠!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.84,1:09:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜你在你自己的城堡里都不能称王
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.14,1:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,！@#￥%……&打扑克的说法,  我早就跟你说了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.31,1:09:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，格罗瑞亚，  你有没有听说过你的邻居霍华德
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.08,1:09:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟一个住在8街的女人厮混的时候  被她的男人逮了个正着
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.06,1:10:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后...头部中了抢.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.69,1:10:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是从他后面开枪的.  - 得了，别再说了.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.03,1:10:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，也许那是他自己作的.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.47,1:10:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些傻货们应该要意识到
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.54,1:10:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑鬼不能在继续这样下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.64,1:10:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在整个国家到处危机四伏
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.61,1:10:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些该死的怒火中烧的黑鬼们随时都会爆发
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.21,1:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 我希望你们全部都待在电话边上
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.51,1:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打电话给有色人种促进协会，种族平等大会等等
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.88,1:10:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是找那些能听得进去你们说话的组织
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.55,1:10:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮助我把那些黑鬼们从街上弄走
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.92,1:10:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴克, 我闻到你的臭屁股的味儿了!  你他奶奶的还在等什么呢?!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.19,1:10:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝呀
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.26,1:10:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔，给我拿点儿该死的西梅汁来.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.10,1:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿不定主意究竟该拿那个  马尔科姆.艾克斯怎么办（美国黑人领袖）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.20,1:10:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他究竟在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.87,1:10:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有一个比马丁路德金更好的计划
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.04,1:10:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人将他们的手伸向你  那么就送他们进墓地里吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.41,1:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那就是所谓的更好的计划?  - 我们准备要走了.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.71,1:10:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜,凯拉美.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.18,1:11:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 晚安.  - 晚安.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.72,1:11:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.92,1:11:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你生气是因为他提到了你爸爸，是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.03,1:11:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.10,1:11:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他提到了很多有关做屋内服务的黑鬼的问题
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.26,1:11:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你生气了.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.37,1:11:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸不是做屋内服务的黑鬼.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.44,1:11:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他是个男仆, 不是吗?  - 别跟我提我爸.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.48,1:11:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没提你爸，对吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.01,1:11:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我所做的一切  我爸爸都会觉得很骄傲
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.76,1:11:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.14,1:12:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在塞尔玛市,所有人都前往教堂为孩子们筹款
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.41,1:12:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有去. 我不想把钱捐给他们  好让他们害死我儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.39,1:12:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子们又一次失败了.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.26,1:12:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一次惨痛的事件，新闻报道将之称为 "血色星期天"
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.40,1:12:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只有少数几个人塞尔玛市  （参见1961年的塞尔玛大桥事件）
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.47,1:12:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个小型的游行队伍穿过塞尔玛市中心
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.24,1:13:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有被阻止...  - ... 迫击炮和火箭筒...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.14,1:13:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...在对康天进行日以继夜地  （越南美军基地）
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.31,1:13:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行毁灭性的炮火打击.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.11,1:13:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的地面部队无法进入...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.94,1:13:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...这是一个完全不同的故事.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.88,1:13:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骑警协助驱散游行的人群.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.71,1:13:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游行队伍曾一度被冲散...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.58,1:13:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的儿子们怎么样，塞西尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.79,1:13:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太了解我大儿子的情况,  总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.40,1:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他可能也在塞尔玛市
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.83,1:13:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，你知道  有时候我觉得
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.44,1:13:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他，就好像生活在  截然不同的两个世界里
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.97,1:13:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望他能安然无恙
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.41,1:13:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...游行队伍被催泪瓦斯烧伤,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.28,1:13:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裸露的伤口和骨折
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.02,1:13:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被送去医院进行治疗...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.58,1:13:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一个美国公民都有平等的权利去投票
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.46,1:13:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管，在这个国家的很多地方  还存在着严峻的不公的事实
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.96,1:14:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们无法进行投票
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.53,1:14:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其原因仅仅是因为他们是黑鬼.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.23,1:14:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"黑鬼?"
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.10,1:14:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是从什么时候开始叫我们黑鬼的?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.64,1:14:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个黑鬼用这个词的频率比我还高
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.91,1:14:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是说真的，我们所有人...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.68,1:14:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...必须要解决这一极其不公正的....
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.85,1:14:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造成了严重后果的历史遗留问题
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.05,1:14:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会做到的.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.80,1:14:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起初是接二连三的火力压制,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.73,1:14:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发起了一次冲锋.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.77,1:14:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海军陆战队开始
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.50,1:14:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行闪电袭击
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.30,1:14:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，嘿, LBJ!（LBJ=约翰逊总统）
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.24,1:14:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天杀了多少个孩子?!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.61,1:14:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，嘿, LBJ!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.81,1:14:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天杀了多少个孩子?!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.71,1:14:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...古老的皇城.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.38,1:14:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它对越南人的意义就相当于  波士顿对于美国人的意义
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.82,1:14:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国家的许多领导者出生于那里  或者在那里接受教育
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.82,1:14:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他们能闭嘴.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.86,1:15:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狙击枪的子弹穿过了这所建筑厚厚的墙壁
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.16,1:15:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小组有一名士兵死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.20,1:15:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能一共有2名或者3名阻击手
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.57,1:15:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲在墙壁后的某个地方.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.94,1:15:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在街道左面还有一架重机枪.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.47,1:15:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金博士，也许你也想发烧躺个几天吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.84,1:15:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰逊总统在越南犯了一个悲剧性的错误
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.62,1:15:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挪开点儿, 大PP.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.42,1:15:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们不去越南打仗?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.69,1:15:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最起码，越共不会叫我们黑鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.06,1:15:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认真点说，你们的父母中有多少人会支持战争?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.86,1:15:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的上帝呀.  为什么你们的父母会支持战争呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.47,1:15:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们并没有很明确地谈过  但是我知道他们会支持的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.77,1:15:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸是做什么的?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.08,1:15:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是一名男仆
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.45,1:15:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑人佣人在我们的历史中扮演着非常重要的角色
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.78,1:16:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说那个，并不是让你取笑我的.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.05,1:16:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟，黑人佣人一直在以他们辛勤工作的态度
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.92,1:16:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和可以信赖的忠诚  在对抗种族偏见
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.10,1:16:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在以他的强烈的职业道德和  高贵的品格
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.13,1:16:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐地驳斥和瓦解着所谓的种族仇恨
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.38,1:16:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，我们在批评那些男仆和女仆们  屈从的态度
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.48,1:16:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在许多方面，他们的确是很顺从  但那是一种无意识的顺从
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.02,1:16:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 请进，塞西尔.  - 下午好，沃纳先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.10,1:16:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您能见我.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.88,1:17:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有色...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.41,1:17:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...因为黑人员工
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.62,1:17:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所做的工作和白人员工所做同样多,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.22,1:17:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信我们的薪水应该也能  体现在我们的服务上面，先生
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.46,1:17:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑人员工?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.40,1:17:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也觉得我们应该能有...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.84,1:17:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...升职的机会.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.11,1:17:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有任何一名黑人男仆
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.84,1:17:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被提拔为技术人员.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.08,1:17:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔，看起来你非常喜欢这里.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.98,1:17:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你对你的薪水和职位不满意
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.15,1:17:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我建议你去其他地方找工作吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.52,1:17:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 恕我冒昧...  - 别让那个马丁路德金的狗屁言论
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.69,1:17:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞得你头脑发热.  别忘记了我是从哪儿找到你的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.00,1:18:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.45,1:18:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.86,1:18:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁.路德.金博士,  和平与非暴力的民权运动的倡导者
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.23,1:18:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在田纳西州孟菲斯市遭遇枪击身亡
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.23,1:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方已经发布了全面通缉凶犯的通告
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.67,1:18:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目击者声称有一名衣着考究的年轻白人男子  匆匆离开案发现场
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.87,1:18:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据报道，警官曾经追捕一辆  安装有无线电装备的车辆
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.84,1:18:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车内载有两名白人男子  并且警方曾向该车辆开火.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.74,1:19:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我是否能活着回到家.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.27,1:19:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我头一次觉得  我并不属于我居住的那个社区.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.05,1:19:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个世界都变了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.98,1:19:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道适合我的地方在哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.25,1:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去的两年里，马丁路德金博士的身份一直是一名男仆
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.89,1:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直游走于白人社区和黑人社区之间
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.29,1:19:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白人并不知道他是谁
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.76,1:19:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是白人最好的朋友死了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.60,1:19:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑人的领路人，我们的摩西
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.26,1:19:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几百年来我们唯一的领路人,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.63,1:19:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也因为痛苦和憎恨  离开了我们
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.30,1:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是此时此刻，我站在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.17,1:19:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都无法允许仇恨涌进我的心中
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.78,1:19:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为仇恨是一种病态的心理.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.62,1:20:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈... 我的房间是粉色的.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.23,1:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得多吃点我做的白薯，卡萝尔.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.46,1:20:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在里边加了橙汁,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.50,1:20:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那会让它们吃起来有股酸酸的味道.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.40,1:20:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩在一起多久了?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.74,1:20:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 5年了.  - 我们俩只是朋友而已.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.71,1:20:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，其余的学生们
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.38,1:21:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也都参与政治活动吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.69,1:21:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都有各自的分工  我们现在有一点点分裂,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.59,1:21:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们中的几个，比如约翰.路易斯  他们还在...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.16,1:21:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我喜欢约翰.路易斯.  - 你怎么知道约翰.路易斯是谁?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.57,1:21:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为，亲爱的，我有读JET杂志
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.63,1:21:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是整天坐在这里  就知道给你缝缝补补
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.70,1:21:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.51,1:21:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经厌倦了待在监狱里的日子.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.24,1:21:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我也一样
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.91,1:21:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金博士的人生观最终  导致了他被谋杀
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.62,1:21:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我们刚刚开始起步的时候  他的那一套很有用
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.85,1:21:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是... 现在已经是时候进行下一步行动了  这就是政治
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.06,1:21:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，你们都要去白宫?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.79,1:21:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，路易斯要去白宫
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.19,1:21:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他们不会让你进去那里的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.73,1:21:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是你还穿着那种袒胸露乳的衣服
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.30,1:21:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你们中的一个人可以进去  但是肯定不会让你们两个都进不去
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.53,1:21:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴. 我们...  我们大部分都是草根平民.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.17,1:21:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以直接跟所有成员联络.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.64,1:21:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们已经成立了我们自己的政党
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.91,1:21:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的政党是什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.41,1:21:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢派对?（Party 双关语）
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.94,1:22:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢派对  你的派对叫什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.62,1:22:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑豹党.（一个左翼黑人民权组织）.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.78,1:22:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么名字啊?  那表示什么意义?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.26,1:22:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们... 为孩子们提供免费的早餐
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.09,1:22:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,免费的医疗诊所, 免费的衣物,  我们还提供自我防御课程.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.20,1:22:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们需要自我防御?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.60,1:22:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会再被他们打败了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.61,1:22:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前几天我和你爸爸  看了一个很棒的电影.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.11,1:22:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那电影让我想起很多有关你的事
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.91,1:22:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.48,1:22:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的，那电影叫什么名字来着?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.51,1:22:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炎热的夜晚  （第40届奥斯卡金像奖最佳影片）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.32,1:22:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炎热的... 夜晚,  是西德尼·波蒂埃演的吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.19,1:22:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪，是西德尼·波蒂埃.  我喜欢西德尼·波蒂埃.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.79,1:22:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西德尼·波蒂埃就是白人们的理想人物  他们希望我们都变成西德尼·波蒂埃那样
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.33,1:22:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在他的电影中，他也在为了平等权在奋斗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.00,1:22:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那种平等只是建立在接受  目前这种以白人主导一切的现状的前提之上
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.07,1:23:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢.  - 可那是行不通的.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.11,1:23:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.07,1:23:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他刚刚赢得了奥斯卡金像奖.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.84,1:23:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他为我们所有人打开了一道屏障
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.98,1:23:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是以白人的方式而已
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.98,1:23:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西德尼·波蒂埃只是一个有钱的汤姆叔叔而已  除此之外他什么都不是
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.15,1:23:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你自己.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.12,1:23:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一幅自负的、愤愤不平的样子
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.53,1:23:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还戴着那么一顶奇形怪状的帽子.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.76,1:23:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到这里,  满嘴跑火车.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.36,1:23:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友还在饭桌上直打嗝
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.13,1:23:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是拿着我给你的钱
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.70,1:23:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都没觉得你应该回去上学
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.31,1:23:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该走了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.74,1:23:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，路易斯  请你离开我的房间
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.55,1:23:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你说什么?  - 你给我滚出我的房间!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.35,1:23:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在做什么?  - 滚出去!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.95,1:23:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他必须得离开!  - 不，塞西尔，不要!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.85,1:23:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我再也无法忍受这一切了!  - 我们不会再见到他了!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.82,1:23:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会再见到他了!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.22,1:23:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后你的生活跟我无关
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.56,1:23:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 现在，大家都坐下  - 我很抱歉，男仆先生
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.16,1:24:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是故意要取笑你的英雄.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.36,1:24:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的生命，以及你所拥有的一切...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.87,1:24:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...都是那个男仆给你的.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.30,1:24:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，带着你那位轻浮的品质低劣的婊子...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.58,1:24:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...滚出这所房子.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.19,1:24:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，我喜欢西德尼·波蒂埃.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.66,1:24:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他演的那部电影叫什么来着?  看看谁来吃晚饭了?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.83,1:24:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.40,1:24:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 卡萝尔来吃晚餐了.  - 嘘，查理.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.01,1:24:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二天，警察带走了路易斯.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.98,1:24:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要害我迟到了.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.25,1:24:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.89,1:24:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还能找谁来保释他出去呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.29,1:25:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次他们又是为了什么把他抓进来的?  坐起来!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.09,1:25:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯说他们抓他是因为
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.86,1:25:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.93,1:25:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他不会再被打败了，所以...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.47,1:25:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...他下了车，并且回击了他们
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.27,1:25:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他的那位小妞呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.34,1:25:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们送她去了医院
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.91,1:25:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医院
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.45,1:25:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查理.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.42,1:25:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些破事必须得停止了.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.09,1:25:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上班要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.22,1:25:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你转告路易斯，我不是他妈.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.29,1:25:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我希望拿回我的钱
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.10,1:25:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.13,1:25:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我没事.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.93,1:25:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢, 卡特叔叔
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.27,1:25:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须得带着你的那些  狗屁黑豹党的东东去其他地方
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.11,1:25:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，我要你把我的钱还给我，你听到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.11,1:25:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的，先生  - 每一分钱.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.01,1:26:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的，先生.  - 喂，叔叔，别告诉我爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.93,1:26:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在监狱里你是如何避开那些性行为的?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.56,1:26:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个什么黑豹党有没有教你那些事?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.80,1:26:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们教你如何坐......
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.41,1:26:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她又开始喝酒了吗?  - 没有，她很清醒.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.54,1:26:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一天到晚什么都不干，除了做缝纫工作  和喂养她的那些鱼
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.98,1:26:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂给它们的比喂给我的还多.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.38,1:26:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去霍华德是不是让你很兴奋?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.02,1:26:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很兴奋因为我不用再回去那里了.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.82,1:26:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么?  - 是的.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.33,1:26:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去越南啦.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.70,1:26:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查理，不要那么做  不要那么做.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.87,1:26:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这个国家对待我们就像是狗一样!  - 那么做什么，做这事儿?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.87,1:26:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在为你的国家而战
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.71,1:27:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我想要为我的国家而战.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.24,1:27:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不会去参加你的葬礼.  - 很好.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.58,1:27:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也不想让你穿着那些亮晶晶的...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.35,1:27:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...奇装异服出现在我的葬礼上
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.72,1:27:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸引走那些原本应该停留在  我的英俊的脸蛋儿的注意力
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.40,1:27:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在怎么称呼你, 路易斯?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.77,1:27:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 闭嘴.  - 路易斯 盖恩斯.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.57,1:27:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查理，闭嘴.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.07,1:27:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要马上知道每一项该死的国内政策,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.04,1:27:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让他们立刻出现在我的书桌上.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.54,1:27:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的.  - 好的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.71,1:27:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你收到上周我们寄给你的备忘录了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.01,1:27:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰和我强烈赞同...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.35,1:27:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一只该死的苍蝇,  这里有一只该死的苍蝇.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.25,1:27:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 天哪.  - 约翰和我都认为
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.09,1:27:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在需要采取善意忽视的策略.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.69,1:27:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 善意忽视?  - 是的.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.99,1:27:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢那个.我喜欢那个.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.63,1:27:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道, 媒体的那些猪们  都把我们描述成恐怖分子了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.30,1:27:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖份子是指那些恐吓和威胁他人的人
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.80,1:28:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是被恐吓的人.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.54,1:28:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我们在大街上在商店里  都不敢讲话的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.61,1:28:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们如何才能和平共处呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.81,1:28:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，现在的黑人权利运动正在进行，对吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.35,1:28:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对.  - 假如我们...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.39,1:28:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如尼克松决定推动和提升黑人的权利
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.66,1:28:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说，支持黑人企业家  只要我们找到合适的支持他们的方式
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.73,1:28:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而把废除种族歧视的责任推卸给法院
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.26,1:28:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那将可以使我们赢得20%的选票
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.97,1:28:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且会打破目前这种僵持的局面
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.87,1:28:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这招太高了，先生.  - 绝对的.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.14,1:28:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你永远都不知道你的顶棚什么时候会塌  因为你的平民窟老板...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.47,1:28:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在忙着四处收取他的房租支票呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.14,1:28:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会帮你修理你的屋顶
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.18,1:28:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是时候该表明立场和采取行动
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.98,1:28:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来对抗这些已困扰我们很久了的不公.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.65,1:28:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们抓走我们中的一个人  那我们就要抓走他们中的两个人.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.35,1:28:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对.  - 现在是时候了.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.15,1:28:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只需要确定  所谓的尼克松黑人权利
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.09,1:28:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不等于尼克松 + 黑豹党
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.16,1:28:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗?  你没有读过胡佛的上一个备忘录?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.00,1:29:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那就是我说的重点.  - 太可怕了.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.33,1:29:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不. 我已经给他开了一路绿灯  让他去找出那些婊子养的黑豹党
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.93,1:29:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很好.  - 绝对的.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.44,1:29:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把他们都弄在一起  然后把它们都丢进升降机井.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.54,1:29:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会说我无所不知.  但是我向你们保证..
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.45,1:29:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...他们总是很惧怕拿着枪的黑鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.39,1:29:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他事吗, 总统先生?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.77,1:29:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天早晨我们要带多少孩子去餐馆?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.47,1:29:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概25至30个吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.60,1:29:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这25至30个孩子本来可以去学校
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.21,1:29:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专心上课.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.31,1:29:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因为他们不想让我们有能力养活我们的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.88,1:29:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们不想让我们有能力保护我们自己
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.99,1:30:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.72,1:30:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我们是在做我们的社区服务
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.56,1:30:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是社区服务.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.26,1:30:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"有人杀了我们中的一个,  我们要杀了他们中的两个?"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.83,1:30:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是社区保护.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.67,1:30:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你准备好去杀人了吗, 卡萝尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.97,1:30:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还没有准备好
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.58,1:30:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.42,1:30:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有爱过我，宝贝?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.98,1:31:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天， 在警察和黑豹党交火后的第二天
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.25,1:31:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察又击毙了两名黑豹党成员  他们包围了黑豹党成员的公寓...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.45,1:31:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...过去一年里，警方一共击毙了26名黑豹党成员
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.55,1:31:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可能也表示警方将会
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.96,1:31:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在全国范围对黑豹党进行彻底地剿灭
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.39,1:31:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方也宣布了......
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.66,1:31:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且强调指出黑豹党....
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.53,1:31:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨，宝贝  - 嗨.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.30,1:31:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 生日快乐.  - 祝我生日快乐呀?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.47,1:31:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快乐.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.94,1:31:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻, 我想要的生日礼物就在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.87,1:31:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，你现在就想要吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.34,1:32:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，你知道的...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.41,1:32:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就在这里?  - 孩子在楼上还是在楼下...?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.35,1:32:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这所房子里再也有没有孩子了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.48,1:32:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你做了一只生日蛋糕.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.38,1:32:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃的蛋糕就在这里啦.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.52,1:32:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦，你个疯子.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.39,1:32:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准备了一些香槟  正在冷冻室冰镇着呢
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.39,1:32:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一些冰淇淋  要吃点吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.36,1:32:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我一起喝吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.19,1:32:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我不喝酒的.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.20,1:32:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喝酒
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.20,1:32:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在逗你玩啦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.70,1:32:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看你扭几下，快点儿啦.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.24,1:32:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，天哪!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.35,1:32:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天有没有收到查理的来信?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.45,1:32:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.62,1:32:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有?  - 查理一直没有音讯.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.49,1:32:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道. 我有个主意.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.59,1:32:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得今晚我们应该去Shantay跳舞
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.86,1:32:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，不. 我都这把年纪了  已经不适合去跳迪斯科了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.10,1:32:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还不老啦，走吧.  我们还没那么老.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.43,1:32:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想去跳迪斯科
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.33,1:32:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的儿子们走来  现在只剩下你和我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.23,1:33:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我，我们俩现在自由了  噢，我都忘记这个东东了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.44,1:33:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，看着这个小小的生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.01,1:33:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你上楼去换上它
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.95,1:33:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 穿上?  - 对，去穿上.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.05,1:33:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧.  - 迅速点.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.95,1:33:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便把我的针线包拿下来  可能我得帮你改一改
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.36,1:33:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迅速点!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.56,1:33:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.90,1:33:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，你在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.81,1:33:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.71,1:33:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该回头再打给我  因为现在这个时间不太合适
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.04,1:33:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他在家.  - 很合适呀!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.31,1:33:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 今晚我们要出去咯.  - 哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.98,1:33:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他在家，而且...  - 你还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.08,1:33:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你没事吧?  - 那是谁?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.92,1:33:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回头打给我.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.16,1:33:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吗?  - 噢，是路易斯呀.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.19,1:33:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他又打电话来要钱?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.33,1:34:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，路易斯
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.33,1:34:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我过生日的时候可没指望你打电话来
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.30,1:34:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该为自己感到羞耻.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.40,1:34:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是个成年人了  居然还打电话跟你妈妈要钱
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.27,1:34:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜猜怎么着?  这可都是男仆先生的钱.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.98,1:34:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是汤姆叔叔的钱
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.68,1:34:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，今天他一个子儿都不会给你的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.35,1:34:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.49,1:34:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.20,1:34:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找错地方了.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.21,1:34:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好错地方了.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.99,1:35:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻译： @ 塔拉Tala
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.18,1:35:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越南带走了我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.02,1:35:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打一开始我就不明白为什么我们要去那里
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.18,1:36:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸还活着吗 ,塞西尔 ?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.89,1:36:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，先生
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.02,1:36:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是孩子的时候他就死了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.53,1:36:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还想要点什么吗，总统先生?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.37,1:36:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，过来坐下.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.49,1:36:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐, 你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.18,1:37:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近一段时间，有关让我辞职下台...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.27,1:37:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...等等这类说法比比皆是  但是我只想让你知道
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.40,1:37:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是绝对不会发生的.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.90,1:37:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过这事儿，会让我变得前所未有的强大
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.78,1:37:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还想要点儿什么吗...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.58,1:37:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...总统先生?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.92,1:37:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯在这里, 他在找你.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.93,1:37:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 大家都很担心你.  - 我读完大学了.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.47,1:37:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿到了社会学的硕士学位
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.85,1:37:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇噢，我就说嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.98,1:37:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好读书.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.44,1:37:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他来了!  好吧，你们俩好好聊吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.61,1:38:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特，你不需要离开.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.70,1:38:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨，爸爸  - 离开这里，路易斯.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.50,1:38:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸爸...  - 我说了，你走吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.17,1:38:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续做好你在做的事
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.43,1:38:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，卡特叔叔.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.77,1:38:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要那么做? 啊?  那是不对的.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.40,1:38:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子也一样受到了伤害  他只是在设法振作起来.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.27,1:38:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他应该受到伤害,卡特.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.49,1:38:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他甚至都没有去参加他弟弟的葬礼.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.45,1:38:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是狗屎一坨  他就没做对过任何事.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.49,1:38:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他刚刚拿到了他的硕士学位  你还想让他怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.50,1:38:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的每一个白头发都是为他操心操的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.56,1:39:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年又一年，时间缓慢地在流逝,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.81,1:39:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是深植于我内心深处的痛苦却从未消失
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.57,1:39:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过了那么多事以后  我和路易斯再也没有讲过话
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.20,1:39:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是上帝庇佑下的一个国家,  所以，我发过誓...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.27,1:39:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，我们有一半石油都依靠进口...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.69,1:40:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对每一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.90,1:40:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及我们的国家的精神和灵魂都是一次打击
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.32,1:40:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有人来了.  - 别担心.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.15,1:40:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩个,  待在家里直到你们感觉好一点再来
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.99,1:40:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的， 巴纳，我会带在家里  但是那也无法让我感觉更好
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.83,1:40:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们这个街区  我们有百分之九的人都失业在家.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.84,1:40:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个广袤的国家,  还有14%的人生活在贫困线以下
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.63,1:40:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而在那些人之中  60%的人不是黑人就是拉丁裔
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.01,1:40:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，我首要的目标  就是致力于推动国会投票
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.85,1:40:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来改善这种情况  降低那些惊人的数据
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.52,1:40:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.19,1:40:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，嗨.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.11,1:40:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你回电话给我.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.99,1:40:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他损失了多少?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.54,1:40:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.79,1:40:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.58,1:41:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.34,1:41:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，他没有赢.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.13,1:41:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你应该打电话给他
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.68,1:41:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查理过世之后,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.85,1:41:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯过来看过我一次
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.52,1:41:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.73,1:41:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他发现我躺在厨房的地板上.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.32,1:41:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时神志不清.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.74,1:41:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喝多了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.91,1:41:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在卫生间吐得自己全身都是.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.75,1:41:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他帮我清理干净那些污物.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.46,1:41:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他告诉我说  我是世界上最好的...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.59,1:41:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都向往的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.68,1:41:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想, 现在...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.77,1:42:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...他一定很想听到他爸爸的声音.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.56,1:42:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你应该打电话给他.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.65,1:42:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.49,1:42:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.95,1:42:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.12,1:42:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.04,1:42:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你待在那里，我过去找你.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.04,1:42:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我... 有一个...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.75,1:42:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...秘密任务要交给你.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.55,1:42:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.01,1:42:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想寄一些钱给那些写信给我...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.47,1:42:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面临财政问题的人们
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.80,1:42:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的职员一直在试着阻止我这么做.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.97,1:42:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以帮助我继续做这件事吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.89,1:42:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题，总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.81,1:42:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激你能这么做.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.57,1:42:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有，请不要告诉南茜
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.44,1:42:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会的.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.03,1:42:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 早上好，塞西尔.  - 早上好，沃纳先生
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.54,1:43:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以坐下吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.01,1:43:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到现在为止  我在这里工作已经超过20年了.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.35,1:43:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去的这些年  黑人员工所拿到的薪水
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.35,1:43:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直比白人员工的薪水低很多
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.61,1:43:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就只觉得这是不对的，沃纳先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.37,1:43:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，这里有很多黑人男仆  都应该成为工程师
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.37,1:43:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实许多年前他们就应该升职了.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.00,1:43:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么认为吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.67,1:44:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也应该拿到和白人员工同等的薪水
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.51,1:44:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就只好离开了.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.48,1:44:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我猜你最好还是走人吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.07,1:44:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你的意思转达给总统先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.16,1:44:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他让我转告你，他会亲自着手处理这事儿的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.37,1:44:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.47,1:44:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆，我不喜欢那些提倡强硬的外交政策...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.18,1:44:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的鹰派人物整天围着罗尼转
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.89,1:44:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要更多的温和派成员在他身边  还有，这次与俄国人的峰会.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.22,1:44:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们打算撬动这座冰山
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.56,1:44:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗尼就必须要跟他们亲自会面
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.06,1:44:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 塞西尔.  - 是，里根夫人?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.73,1:44:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们回头再谈，吉姆.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.57,1:44:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.40,1:44:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里非常受欢迎呀.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.82,1:45:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都说是你让他们  得到了升职和加薪的机会
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.41,1:45:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我居然都对此全然不知.  - 我希望我能接受这份功劳.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.87,1:45:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想邀请你参加下周举行的国宴
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.63,1:45:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我会在那里的，里根先生.  - 不
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.17,1:45:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是... 不是作为男仆，塞西尔.  我是邀请你作为宾客出席国宴.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.88,1:45:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是总统先生会更希望我亲自为他服务
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.05,1:45:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别担心那个，至于罗尼  我会照顾他的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.97,1:45:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们下周见  请带上你的夫人.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.81,1:45:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我夫人?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.65,1:45:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她... 她叫格罗瑞亚, 对吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.78,1:45:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对，夫人.  - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.45,1:45:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.63,1:45:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是门厅.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.80,1:46:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.78,1:46:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帮你拿杯香槟吗, 盖恩斯先生?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.57,1:46:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 闭嘴吧你  - 好的.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.41,1:46:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士们先生们,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.21,1:46:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国总统和第一夫人.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.98,1:46:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在这个桌子旁服务  和坐在这里的感觉是那么地不同
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.86,1:47:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常不同.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.70,1:47:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看到那些男仆们在服务时的  那张与平时完全的痛的脸孔
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.79,1:47:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道在我的一生中，  我也始终以两张面孔示人
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.63,1:47:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格罗瑞亚看起来很开心  但是我并不觉得.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.05,1:47:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜我所希望的是，我们能真的坐在那里  而不是为了作秀
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.40,1:47:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜大家都胃口都很好
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.15,1:47:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你娘的...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.49,1:47:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想就这个问题表明我自己的态度
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.50,1:48:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果国会要让对南非的制裁决议通过
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.09,1:48:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将不得不否决这些制裁决议.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.55,1:48:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统先生，我们觉得那会是一个绝对的错误
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.89,1:48:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南非对黑人平民残酷镇压的行为
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.77,1:48:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经使得这一问题  不再单纯停留在外交政策的层面
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.73,1:48:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是牵扯到美国对于种族问题的态度
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.48,1:48:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是属于你自己的党派的参议员.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.40,1:48:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为什么我们很想让你知道
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.53,1:48:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南非现在存在很严重的人权问题
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.74,1:48:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑人常年遭受欺压和折磨
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.45,1:48:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至在大街上都会遭到枪击
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.62,1:48:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国人可以从电视上看到这一切,  种族隔离让他们感到震惊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.54,1:48:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做出决定了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.42,1:48:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统先生，你作为世界领导者的声望  已经受到了影响
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.05,1:48:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就种族问题而言...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.59,1:48:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国需要站在历史正确的一面
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.93,1:48:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一遍.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.93,1:48:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果国会会通过这个法案,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.02,1:49:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会提出否定
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.86,1:49:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,句号.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.99,1:49:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 你又在读书?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.00,1:49:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点起来，在我射飞你的小脑袋之前  快点把这些盘子都洗干净.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.26,1:49:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那次晚宴之后  好像我周围的任何事看起来都不对劲了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.27,1:49:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总是感到很困惑.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.21,1:50:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们开始把那些有关路易斯
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.30,1:50:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他的朋友们所做的事情  写成文章，写成书
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.02,1:50:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯不再是一名罪犯.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.23,1:50:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他变成了一名英雄,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.73,1:50:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成了一名为了拯救我们国家的灵魂的斗士
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.25,1:50:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要来电而饼干吗?  - 谢谢你，先生.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.25,1:50:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 饼干.  - 谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.21,1:50:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饼干?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.80,1:50:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你  - 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.92,1:50:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.55,1:50:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饼干?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.48,1:51:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很喜欢我的工作.  但是现在却觉得有点儿不同
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.20,1:51:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是不是每一个老人  都会有失落和无助的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.58,1:51:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是. 我是那么地失落
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.67,1:51:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么地无助
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.34,1:51:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国人对于我们对自己人所犯下的错误
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.60,1:51:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是采取视而不见的态度
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.64,1:51:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却很喜欢对其他国家的事指手画脚
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.60,1:51:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们听说了那些集中营的故事,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.73,1:51:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是就在美国，就在我们自己的土地上
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.86,1:51:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的营地却已经存在了200年之久
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.84,1:52:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的爸爸就埋葬在那变边
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.26,1:52:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈一定会以我为荣,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.47,1:52:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我嫁了一个像你这么好的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.43,1:52:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多年一直那么照顾我  那么疼爱我
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.77,1:52:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你，塞西尔 盖恩斯.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.36,1:52:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更爱你，格罗瑞亚
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.17,1:52:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定你要这么做吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.75,1:52:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.67,1:52:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想第一个告诉你
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.68,1:53:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你是这里最棒的男仆.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.43,1:53:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说，你就像家人一样，塞西尔
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.89,1:53:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能服侍你是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.65,1:53:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是我，我可以代表所有的总统说
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.02,1:53:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为你的国家提供了最好的服务
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.49,1:53:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，总统先生
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.16,1:53:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.75,1:53:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有关所有的这些民权问题...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.01,1:53:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我会害怕我...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.30,1:53:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在了错误的一面, 嗯....我...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.97,1:53:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...做错了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.22,1:53:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我觉得我很害怕  那些事情所蕴含的真正的意义
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.44,1:53:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我会试着不要再害怕.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.07,1:53:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们想让谁获得自由?!  - 曼德拉!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.86,1:54:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想让谁获得自由?!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.24,1:54:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 立刻!  - 释放曼德拉!!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.74,1:54:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20年前, 我们在这个国家为争取我们的权利而游行
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.41,1:54:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天，我们游行是为了为南非的同胞争取自由
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.50,1:54:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.04,1:54:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗纳德.里根在  攻击和破坏我们的每一项
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.76,1:54:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在进行的民权计划
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.93,1:54:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对!  - 对i!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.47,1:54:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在以他的种族问题的政策来
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.31,1:54:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,协助压迫南非的黑人  我说的对吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.98,1:54:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我说得对吗?  - 对!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.40,1:54:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.78,1:54:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯蒂文，斯蒂文在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.69,1:54:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 释放曼德拉!  - 释放曼德拉!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.70,1:54:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,释放曼德拉!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.28,1:54:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,释放曼德拉!  释放曼德拉!释放曼德拉!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.63,1:55:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.05,1:55:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，路易斯
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.14,1:55:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.56,1:55:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里和你一起抗议.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.40,1:55:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会被逮捕的，爸爸  你会丢了你的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.32,1:55:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我弄丢了你
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.33,1:55:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.34,1:55:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.41,1:56:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心，爸爸  几个小时后我们就会出去的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.29,1:56:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁说我会担心的?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.25,1:56:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我离开监狱以后  我想我已经明白了一切
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.05,1:56:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还好吗，爸爸?  - 嗯，不，不，我没事.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.97,1:56:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我从未想像过我会见到...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.60,1:56:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...一个黑人
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.85,1:56:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会真的成为一名美国总统的竞选人
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.15,1:56:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.36,1:56:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是甜玉米.  - 那个玉米看上去看不错.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.09,1:57:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上，格罗瑞亚和我都会  去我们的投票地点...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.38,1:57:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是在那里  为贝拉克·奥巴马投出了我们的选票
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.10,1:57:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是坐在那里, 看着，笑着.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.06,1:57:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你吃完了吗?  - 差不多了.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.27,1:57:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，我们该走了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.99,1:57:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在照片里看起来非常棒.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.86,1:57:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，亲爱的.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.12,1:57:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么路易斯的妻子要给那个孩子取名叫...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.33,1:57:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ... 史旷达?  - 现在可别再提这茬儿了.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.33,1:57:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又没提啦, 我只是不太明白  那名字究竟是个啥意思
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.75,1:57:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说真的啦，史旷达?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.43,1:57:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她起那么名字可能就是为了气我
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.59,1:57:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有任何人会做任何事来气你啦.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.51,1:57:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，她肯定是.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.23,1:58:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就是一个丑陋的小丫头  你瞧她那个扁扁的塌鼻子
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.98,1:58:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我希望她的鼻子能再长大一点  - 别再唠叨那个啦.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.23,1:58:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你知道你不应该那么想啦  - 难道你不觉得..
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.28,1:58:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的嘴巴有点儿像路易斯?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.32,1:58:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得... 她看起来就跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.45,1:58:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 像我?  - 对，所以你得...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.45,1:58:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...你得停止再那么谈论她.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.37,1:58:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我再看看她，嗯，很好
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.84,1:58:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看起来是有点儿像我.  她是个漂亮的小东西.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.43,1:58:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我可以接受史旷达这个名字
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.85,1:58:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了我把我的圣经放哪儿了.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.10,1:58:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你知道我需要我的圣经  - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.98,1:58:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我想我可能把它忘在洗手间了.  - 路易斯为什么迟到了?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.98,1:58:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从他当选议员之后...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.07,1:58:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...就很少能按时带我们去教堂了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.62,1:58:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我都不敢相信你还在... 发牢骚.  - 我看他连去参加他自己的葬礼都会迟到
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.75,1:59:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在为路易斯的事... 感到烦躁?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.58,1:59:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说了他会来这里接我们.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.46,1:59:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去吧，打电话给他.  - 我才不会打电话给路易斯.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.80,1:59:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要拿上我的钱包，还有...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.89,1:59:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么? 以赛亚书?（圣经旧书）
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.35,1:59:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你.. 在这里做了标记.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.73,1:59:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意得把我绊倒在地
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.02,1:59:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝，你得...  把它挪到另一边.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.33,1:59:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.88,1:59:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.84,1:59:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你睡着了?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.39,2:00:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.35,2:00:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.59,2:00:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...投票站即将关闭,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.63,2:00:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是胜算比较大的州,  特别是加利福尼亚
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.88,2:00:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加州美国最大的州,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.05,2:00:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有55张选票.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.84,2:00:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在夏威夷州, 那是巴拉克·奥巴马出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.80,2:00:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里的投票站也即将关闭.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.68,2:00:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱达荷, 俄勒冈，还有华盛顿州
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.10,2:00:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近几年，这些州在总统竞选的过程中
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.40,2:00:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,始终在坚持推行民主竞选
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.69,2:00:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么马上
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.32,2:00:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些州也即将关闭他们的投票站
Dialogue: 0,2:00:54.61,2:00:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们大致可以推测出...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.36,2:00:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:59.36,2:01:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...这是一个预测.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.37,2:01:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个众人已期待许久的时刻...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.75,2:01:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯, 下来，快下来!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.37,2:01:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...也有可能是极具历史意义的一个时刻
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.29,2:01:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此刻，CNN基本可以推测出...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:15.01,2:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现年47岁的巴拉克·奥巴马
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.63,2:01:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会成为美国的总统当选人
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.89,2:01:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们预计...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.26,2:01:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些对于....  “在美国任何事情都有可能发生”
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.39,2:01:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一说法持怀疑态度的人...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.52,2:01:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些想知道我们先辈的梦想是否还存在的人
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.07,2:01:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些对我们的民主的力量心怀疑虑的人
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.32,2:01:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚，你将会得到回答
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.02,2:02:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要通过他们的眼睛...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.11,2:02:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...看出他们在想什么...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:59.28,2:03:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...看出他们需要什么...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.91,2:03:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...预测...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.95,2:03:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...要让你的服务对像露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,2:03:21.47,2:03:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖恩斯先生.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.34,2:03:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿德米拉尔.罗尚, 首席接待员.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.93,2:03:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很高兴见到你，阿德米拉尔.  - 无比荣幸，先生.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.03,2:03:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想告诉你能见到是多么地荣幸，先生
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.49,2:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.20,2:03:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统非常期待能见到你.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:50.12,2:03:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.71,2:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...那很好，不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.38,2:03:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我为你带路
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.38,2:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道怎么走.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.68,2:04:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核心问题是,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.68,2:04:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否所有的美国人都享有同等的权利
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.01,2:04:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和同等的就业机会
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.85,2:04:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是美国黑人为了保护  他们自己的权益...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.40,2:04:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和实现所谓的美国梦  所付出的努力和取得的成就
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.15,2:04:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将用那历经时间考验的
Dialogue: 0,2:04:28.08,2:04:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振奋我们精神的不朽信条回应他们:
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.37,2:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我们可以.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.45,2:04:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谨以这部影片献给那些为了我们的自由  以及为了我们的公民权利而奋斗的人们
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.99,2:12:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本片涉及的历史事件较多，如翻译过程中存在疏漏，请多多谅解.  翻译： @塔拉Tala
